\id JDG - Mbembe Okohm
\h Nnwẹr kw'Asi-aponga
\toc2 Nnwẹr kw'Asi-aponga
\toc1 Nnwẹr kw'Asi-aponga
\mt1 Nnwẹr kw'Asi-aponga
\ip Nnwẹr nwa okpen Nnwẹr kw'Asi-aponga. Odem kwa nnwẹr nwa ode odem kw'okhuri anọng p'iwa Ibinọkpaabyi om-otzekha anọng bi, bẹ ade asi-aponga k'Israẹl tzọni k'obo kwa Joshua maa, apyiri k'ittẹwọr s'ogbe kw'avaar p'Israẹl k'ogbe kwa Samuẹl ọdabhi. Iwa ode ogbe kw'ẹkhọma ch'Israẹl ekk'eho ẹgaangi ẹnang echekhi ch'Ibinọkpaabyi. Kaambi ode bi, wa anọng p'Israẹl akk'echikhi bi, bẹ ahok echekhi ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, wa bẹ akk'nnam akpa abọra Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, an-akpobha ekpo ẹdọdọk. Wa ọnọng kpenamkpen on-orukhi akpen k'odem kw'ọdaakh-ẹ. Ndori s'atzim pa nnwẹr sẹ nde bi: wani, wa anọng akpa nnam abọra Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi; mfa, wa Ibinọkpaabyi om-otzima ẹfa ch'okhekhenmon ọnang bẹ etuma; nttaan, wa anọng mba am-abhom ẹkkaana anang Ibinọkpaabyi; nna, wa Ibinọkpaabyi ọbhaanga ẹmọng nda, otzekha ọkkaan kw'ode osi-aponga kwa bẹ. Ọnọng kw'orong ọkkẹri kwa nnwẹr nwa kode, yina, immaana-dik rani s'abaJew ichibhi bi, Samuẹl wọ ọkkẹri Nnwẹr kw'Asi-oponga.
\c 1
\s1 Anọng p'Israẹl arim anọng pa Kenaan p'arikhi abẹ
\p 
\v 1 K'ogbe kw'iwa Joshua ọkk'ọpa, anọng p'Israẹl abọbh Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi bi, “Bọng ẹkhọma chaman dọ échi eden ẹtza erima anọng pa Kenaan abẹ o?”
\p 
\v 2 Iwa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi obhina bi, “Ẹkhọma cha Juda dọ échi eden; kaam nkk'irerek na ndọkha nge ka mbọhk sabẹ.”
\p 
\v 3 Mẹ wọ ofon, anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Juda aben anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Simeọn p'ade ayokh-obhon pabẹ p'Israẹl bi, “Bọng kwu tzọn man abẹ, mochina k'ẹkhọma cha bẹ akkem anang man, ifha mọtza orima anọng pa Kenaan abẹ. Maman óbiro ọ́tzọn bọng abẹ ochina k'okhubha kwa bọng.” Mando kw'anọng pa Simeọn atzọni bẹ abẹ.
\p 
\v 4 Mando kw'anọng pa Juda atza arim egbong nda. Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi osi anọng pa Juda akhema anọng pa Kenaan ọmaana anọng pa Pẹriz. Wa bẹ afhu anọng nnọhna ẹrọbh obhiri nzen ka Bẹzẹk.
\v 5 Mẹ wọ kw'iwa bẹ are Adoni-Bẹzẹk kw'ode ọvaarnọng kwa Bẹzẹk abira arim-ẹ abẹ, bẹ abira akhema anọng pa Kenaan ọmaana anọng pa Pẹriz.
\v 6 Wa Adoni-Bẹzẹk ọrọbh. Bẹ akhubh-ẹ abira abọkh-ẹ, bẹ akpaar-ẹ nnọnna-dim sa mbọhk ọmaana sa mmo.
\p 
\v 7 Mẹ wọ ofon, Adoni-Bẹzẹk oben bi, “Avaarnọng arọbh attaan obhiri jobh pa bẹ akpaar nnọnna-dim sa mbọhk ọmaana sa mmo, akk'abiribiri p'ẹchakpo adungi k'okpokkoro kwaam irekhirek. Ma, Ibinọkpaabyi ọkk'aam ọsa mach'iwa nsi bẹ.” Wa bẹ atzin-ẹ atzima achina ka Jẹrusalẹm, ọtza ope kẹ.
\p 
\v 8 Iwa ajinọng p'ẹkhọma cha Juda abira arima anọng pa Jẹrusalẹm abẹ, akhema bẹ. Wa bẹ atzima ọkkaangkkaang afhu anọng p'odedenmon nwa, bẹ abira akhe obhon ekpon.
\p 
\v 9 Ayongi mẹ, anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Juda ahakha atza arima anọng pa Kenaan abẹ, p'arukhi k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho ka Nẹgẹv ọmaana k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho sa ndẹr-ọtzẹri, k'okhubha kw'ewuchen em-eyin.
\v 10 Wa anọng pa Juda atza arima anọng pa Kenaan p'arukhi ka Hẹbrọn (kw'iwa okpen Kiriyat-Arba). Bẹ abira akhema Shẹshayi ọmaana Ahiman ttara Talmayi.
\v 11 Bẹ afona mẹ atza arima anọng p'arukhi ka Dẹbir (kw'iwa okpen Kiriyat-Sẹphẹr).
\p 
\v 12 Iwa Kalẹb oben bi, “Ojinọng kpenamkpen kw'orim Kiriyat-Sẹphẹr abẹ, obiro okhem-ẹ, kaam ńnang-ẹ Aksa kw'ode ominanwa kwaam k'ọbada.”
\v 13 Wa Otniyẹl kw'ode nnwa kw'ijinọng kwa Kẹnaz, kw'iwa ode ọgbaanotte kw'ikhakhari kwa Kalẹb, okhema obhon nwa. Mando kwa Kalẹb ọtzọk ominanwa kwẹ Aksa ọnang-ẹ k'ọbada.
\p 
\v 14 Iwa ewu dani, Aksa okwu okhebha Otniyẹl, ọchọhma Otniyẹl bi ọtza ophyem otte kwa kẹ Aksa irerek. Mada Aksa ọhak k'ẹnyanyaang chẹ, Kalẹb ọbọbh-ẹ bi, “Mbọng f'áror bi nsi nnang-ọ o?”
\p 
\v 15 Mẹ wọ ofon, Aksa obhina bi, “Kọ si-m ittabọhng. Mada akk'aam irerek ananga ka Nẹgẹv, kọ biri nnang-m akhekhaho.” Mando kwa Kalẹb ọnang-ẹ akhekhaho p'ebira-ebira ọmaana p'ẹrakha-ẹrakha.
\p 
\v 16 Iwa va pa va pa Ken kw'ode otte kwa kwanọng kwa Mosẹs, ttara anọng pa Juda abina k'Odedenmon kw'Aji, atza aruk k'ottem kw'anọng p'arukhi k'ebherede cha Juda, ka Nẹgẹv ọbaanga Arad.
\p 
\v 17 Iwa ajinọng p'ẹkhọma cha Juda atzọn anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Simeọn p'ade ayokh-ibhon p'Israẹl, bẹ atza arima anọng pa Kenaan p'arukhi ka Zephat abẹ. Bẹ adimi obhon kwa Zephat biphyir-phyir. Mẹ wọ ofon, bẹ an-ayeri obhon nwa Horma\f + \fr 1.17 \ft K'eHiburu, Horma oyini ekhibhi.\f*.
\v 18 Wa anọng pa Juda abira akhema ibhon sa Gaza ọmaana Ashkẹlọn ttara Ẹkrọn. Wa bẹ abọk odedenmon kpenamkpen ttara enem chẹ.
\p 
\v 19 Iwa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi owobh ttara ajinọng p'ẹkhọma cha Juda. Bẹ akhema okhubha kwa mgbegbeho, yina, wa bẹ anọng p'arukhi k'ittolim kafha akhubh, da iwa bẹ akhaam akpaar pa nnyanyaang mmindọr p'ade akkonga-akkonga.
\v 20 Wa bẹ atzọkha Hẹbrọn anang Kalẹb, kw'okhubhi va pa va p'ijinọng attaan p'Anak, mach'iwa Mosẹs okk'ochekhi.
\v 21 Wa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin, anọng pa Jẹbus p'arukhi ka Jẹrusalẹm kakhubhi; anọng pa Jẹbus atzim arukhi k'ottem kwa anọng pa Bẹnjamin maa, apyiri k'ewu cha mayina.
\p 
\v 22 Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi owobh ttara ẹkhọma cha Josẹph, bẹ atza arima obhon kwa Bẹtẹl abẹ.
\v 23 Mada bẹ atzọhmi nttọ s'ẹhọhmmọr cha Josẹph ka Bẹtẹl (kw'iwa okpen Luz).
\v 24 Nttọ nna nne ojinọng wani kw'om-ofona k'odedenmon oyin ka, bẹ aben-ẹ bi, “Kọ tzibh man eden cha mórenga odim k'obhon ẹtzaanga, maman óbiro ore kwẹ ore bi, mosi ejibha osi ọnang-ọ.”
\v 25 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa ojinọng nwa otzibh bẹ eden, bẹ atzima ọkkangkkaang afhu anọng p'odedenmon. Yina, wa bẹ ojinọng nwa ọmaana ẹhọhmmọr chẹ kafhu.
\v 26 Wa on-ochina k'irerek s'anọng pa Het osi odedenmon mẹ, oyer-ẹ Luz, kw'on-ode che ch'ibe nna maa, apyiri k'ewu cha mayina.
\p 
\v 27 Yina, wa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Manasẹ, anọng pa Bet-Shan ọmaana pa Taanak ọmaana pa Dor ọmaana pa Ibleam ọmaana pa Mẹgido ọttaara abhobhona pabẹ biphyir kakhubhi, da iwa ofon anọng pa Kenaan ka nttem bi, bẹ aruk ka ngọma nna.
\v 28 K'ogbe kw'iwa anọng p'Israẹl akk'ẹfa an-akhaama, bẹ an-asi anọng pa Kenaan asi obira-tzọhm. Yina, wa bẹ anọng mba biphyir kakhubhi.
\v 29 Wa anọng p'ẹkhọma ch'Ephraim anọng pa Kenaan p'arukhi ka Gẹzẹr kabira akhubh, yina, wa anọng pa Kenaan achin ororo aruk ttara bẹ.
\v 30 Wa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Zebulun anọng pa Kanaan p'arukhi ka Kitron ọmaana ka Nahalol kakhubhi. Mẹ wọ ofon, wa anọng pa Kenaan achina ororo aruk k'ottem kwabẹ. Yina, wa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Zebulun an-asi anọng pa Kenaan asi obira-tzọhm.
\v 31 Wa anọng p'ẹkhọma ch'Ashẹr anọng pa Kenaan p'arukhi k'Ako ọmaana ka Sidọn, ọmaana k'Ahlab ọmaana, k'Akzib ọmaana ka Helba, ọmaana k'Aphẹk ọttaara ka Rohob kakhubhi.
\v 32 Ofona mẹ, wa anọng p'ẹkhọma ch'Ashẹr achina ororo aruk ttara anọng pa Kenaan, okhuri da iwa bẹ ani bẹ akhubhi.
\v 33 Anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Naphtali anọng p'arukhi ka Bet-Shẹmẹsh ọmaana ka Bet-Anat kakhubhi, wa bẹ achina ororo abira aruk ttara anọng pa Kenaan. Yina, wa anọng pa Naphtali an-asi anọng pa Kenaan p'arukhi ka Bet-Shẹmẹsh ọmaana ka Bet-Anat asi obira-tzọhm.
\v 34 Wa anọng p'Amọr akpa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Dan amaana k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho, bẹ anọng pa Dan ọbọhk katte ahakha akwu k'ittolim.
\v 35 Wa anọng p'Amọr abira asi achibhi bi, bẹ aruk k'egbegbeho cha Heres, ọmaana k'Aijalọn ọmaana ka Shalbim. Yina, mada iwa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Josẹph akk'ẹfa an-akhaama, bẹ an-asi anọng p'Amọr asi obira-tzọhm.
\v 36 Wa enem ch'ẹkhọma ch'Amọr ẹttẹwọr k'Eden ch'Ininaang, etzima ẹtza epyiri ka Sẹla maa, ẹkwọbha ẹrọhng.
\c 2
\s1 Orenga-eden kw'Ibinọkpaabyi oyin anọng p'Israẹl abẹ
\p 
\v 1 Iwa orenga-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi obina ka Gilgal, ochina ka Bokim oben bi, “Kaam ndim bọng mbina k'Ijip, ndima bọng nchina k'irerek s'iwa nchekhi bi nnang ab'atte. Mben bi, ‘Kaam echekhi cha ngaam ttara bọng, kímbiri mfha mvọhkhi.
\v 2 Bọng kakhaambi asi echekhi ttara anọng p'arukhi m'irerek nna. Yina, bọng akhaambi avọhkhi ọjafọhnibe fabẹ.’ Kaambi mẹ wọ, bọng itzọhng k'atzim paam kayong. Bọng an-asi yan asi mando?
\v 3 Ma, kaam nkk'bọng na mbena bi, ‘Kaam anọng mba kabọng k'itzitzikha kíngwubh; bẹ áde mach'amma amunapẹ anang bọng, ikha sabẹ íbiri íde mach'agbagbara inang bọng.’ ”
\p 
\v 4 Mada oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi okk'anọng p'Israẹl idik nna biphyir ọgbaakha, anọng mba abhom amọng k'ẹrọng.
\v 5 Wa bẹ ayeri ibe nna Bokim\f + \fr 2.5 \ft K'eHiburu, Bokim oyini abhom-ẹmọng.\f*. Bẹ afọhni nja m'ibe nnuma anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi.
\s1 Oho-gaangi kw'osi bẹ akhema anọng p'Israẹl
\p 
\v 6 K'ogbe kwa Joshua okk'anọng p'Israẹl obena bi bẹ abhana, anọng kpenamkpen abhana atza atzọkha irerek s'ide ekkema chabẹ.
\v 7 K'ogbe kw'iwa Joshua orukhi akpen biphyir, ọmaana k'ogbe kw'iwa adeho p'iwa arukhi akpen da Joshua ọkk'ọpa, bẹ abira are odik kpenamkpen kw'iwa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọkk'ọsa ọnang anọng p'Israẹl, wa anọng p'Israẹl akpobha Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi.
\p 
\v 8 Iwa Joshua kw'ode nnwa kwa Nun, obiro ode ọtzọhmnọng kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, ope da ode cho arọbh azen obhiri jobh.
\v 9 Wa bẹ anọhng-ẹ k'irerek s'ide ekkema chẹ, ka Timnat-Sẹra k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim, k'ebira-ebira kw'egbegbeho cha Gaash.
\p 
\v 10 K'ogbe kw'ọgbọ nwa biphyir ọkk'ọpa otzor ab'otte, ọgbọ ọdọdọk ọn-ọbar kw'oni Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọrọbhi, ọmaana idik s'ọkk'ọsa ọnang Israẹl.
\v 11 Wa anọng p'Israẹl asi ebibya k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi bẹ an-akpobha ikha sa Baal.
\v 12 Bẹ akpa nnam abọra Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kw'ab'otte, kw'iwa otzim bẹ obina k'Ijip. Bẹ an-atzor ayokh-ibaanga, akpobha ikha sabẹ. Be ajemi idọdọkhi s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi,
\v 13 okhuri da iwa bẹ akpa nnam abọra Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi an-akpobha ikha sa Baal ọmaana s'Ashtọrẹt.
\v 14 Wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi otzima idọdọkhi otte anọng p'Israẹl ọbọhk ọnang attattaanga-nọng, p'achi bẹ k'egbong. Okpe anọng p'Israẹl ọnang attattaang-nọng pabẹ makhọra, pa bẹ ani abẹ dọk afha abe.
\v 15 Ogbe kpenamkpen kw'anọng p'Israẹl atza egbong, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi otte anọng p'Israẹl ọbọhk ayok akhema bẹ, otzor k'ọnwọhngi kw'ọkk'ọtzọkha. Wa anọng p'Israẹl an-awobh ka dama-dama kw'ideden.
\p 
\v 16 Iwa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọnang anọng p'Israẹl asi-aponga, p'akkaan arọbha bẹ ka mbọhk s'anọng p'achi bẹ k'egbong.
\v 17 Kaambi mẹ wọ, wa anọng mba itzọhng kayong anang asi-aponga pabẹ. Yina, bẹ akpaanga m'ikha s'anọng mba mach'azaaza, am-akpobha ikha. Wa anọng p'Israẹl ajaabhi mmo atte immaana-dik s'ab'otte ọbọhk, ab'otte p'iwa ahak eho anang asana p'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi.
\v 18 K'ogbe kpenamkpen kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi osi ọnọng ọttọhn-aponga, kẹ om-owobha ttar-ẹ, ọkkaana ọrọbha bẹ ka mbọhk s'attattaanga-nọng pabẹ otzor k'odem kw'ọsi-aponga nwa oruk opyiri. Wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọkpa nnam ọbọra idọdọkhi sẹ, okhuri ẹmọng ch'anọng p'Israẹl abhomi, k'ihem s'attattaanga-nọng pabẹ am-anang bẹ.
\v 19 Yina, idikha osi-aponga nwa ope, anọng p'Israẹl akpa nnam k'ọmmaana-tzama kw'opyibhi ọyọhnga kw'ab'otte pabẹ, atza akpobha ikha abira ahakha eho anang sẹ. Wa bẹ for kado bi, bẹ akpa nnam abọra ibibyadik ọmaana ohogaangi.
\p 
\v 20 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọdọkhi ettem otzima otzor anọng p'Israẹl oben bi, “Okhuri da ẹkhọma nda ekk'echekhi chaam cha nkk'nda nnang ab'otte ẹvọhkhi, bẹ itzọhng kabira ayonga anang-m,
\v 21 kaam idibhon sa Joshua ope oji ka bẹ k'itzitzikha kíngwubh.
\v 22 Kaam ndima idibhon nna nyoma anọng p'Israẹl, ifha nne s'ode na bẹ afha aruk akpen atzor ka nden s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi mach'iwa ab'otte arukhi.”
\v 23 Wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi otte idibhon nna ọbọhk iwobha, sẹ k'ogbe wani kokhubhi, da iwa oni sẹ ọbọhk otte ọnang Joshua.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Ma wọ ode idibhon s'iwa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi otte ọbọhk iwobha, ifha otzima oyoma anọng p'Israẹl biphyir, p'iwa ani egbong manda dani k'ẹkhọma cha Kenaan atzima arima.
\v 2 (Wa osi mando ifha otzima mẹ okpebhi va pa va p'anọng p'Israẹl odik okhuri egbong, p'iwa ani egbong arong):
\v 3 wa idibhon nna ide avaar azen pa Philistiya, ọmaana anọng pa Kenaan, ọmaana anọng pa Sidọn, ọmaana anọng pa Hiv p'arukhi ka mgbegbeho sa Lebanọn, ttẹwọr k'egbegbeho cha Baal-Hermọn maa, apyiri ka Lebo-Hamat.
\v 4 Wa otte idibhon nna ọbọhk iwobha k'odem kw'otzima sẹ oyoma anọng p'Israẹl, ifha ore s'ode na bẹ ahokh asana p'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi p'iwa okk'orenga ka Mosẹs ọnang ab'otte.
\p 
\v 5 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl arukhi k'ottem kw'anọng pa Kenaan, ọmaana anọng pa Het, ọmaana anọng p'Amọr, ọmaana anọng pa Pẹriz, ọmaana anọng pa Hiv ttara anọng pa Jẹbus.
\v 6 Wa anọng p'idibhon nna atzọk aminava p'Israẹl k'ọbada, bẹ atzọkha aminava pabẹ anang ajinọng p'Israẹl k'ọbada, bẹ abira akpobha ikha s'idibhon nna.
\s1 Otniyẹl ode ọsi-aponga kw'Israẹl
\p 
\v 7 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl asi epyibha k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, bẹ araama Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kwabẹ. Bẹ abira akpobha agbatza pa Baal ọmaana mkpọmmachi s'Ashẹra.
\v 8 Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọdọkhi ettem otzima otzor anọng p'Israẹl, otte bẹ ọbọhk ọnang ọvaarnọng kwa Kushan-Rishatayim kw'ofon Aram-Naharayim. Mando kw'anọng p'Israẹl asi itzọhm anang Kushan-Rishatayim ka cho azenanttaan.
\v 9 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa anọng p'Israẹl abhomi ẹkkaana anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi. Wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi otzima ọkkaan okwu ọkkaana bẹ. Wa ọkkaan nwa okpen Otniyẹl kw'ode nnwa kwa Kẹnaz, kw'ode ogbaanotte kw'ikhakhari kwa Kalẹb.
\v 10 Wa egwugwuma ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ch'ẹfa ẹnwẹ-ẹ, on-okwu ode osi-aponga kw'Israẹl. Wa ọtza orima egbong ttara ọvaar Kushan-Rishatayim kw'ofon Aram. Mando kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọkkaan Otniyẹl ekhem-ẹ.
\v 11 Mẹ wọ ofon, odidiri okhuna m'irerek nna ka cho arọbh afa, maa, opyiri k'ogbe kwa Otniyẹl kw'ode nnwa kwa Kenaz ope.
\s1 Ehud ode osi-aponga kw'Israẹl
\p 
\v 12 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl abira asi ebibya k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi. Okhuri ebibya nda cha bẹ asi, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọnang Eglọn kw'ode ọvaarnọng kwa Moab ẹfa ch'ọkhem anọng p'Israẹl.
\v 13 Wa Eglọn oben anọng p'Ammọn ọmaana anọng p'Amalẹk bi, bẹ akwu attar-ẹ ifha bẹ atza arima anọng p'Israẹl abẹ. Wa bẹ atzọkha Odedenmon kw'Aji.\f + \fr 3.13 \ft Odedenmon kw'Aji ode Jeriko.\f*
\v 14 Wa anọng p'Israẹl awobh k'irekhirek kw'ẹfa ch'Eglọn kw'ode ọvaarnọng kwa Moab, ka cho chi obhiri attaan.
\p 
\v 15 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl abira abhom ẹmọng anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi. Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọnang bẹ Ehud mach'ọkkaan kwabẹ. Wa Ehud osi ibhiribọhk, ode nnwa kwa Gẹra kw'ofon k'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin. Wa anọng p'Israẹl atzọhm Ehud bi, ochena ọvaar Eglọn kwa Moab nnduma.
\v 16 Wa Ehud ọkk'ọkkangkkaang ọsa, kw'adum pẹ apyiri ọttọhk k'ẹtzọkhi dani, ọjaabhi nnam mfa. Ọtzọkh-ẹ ọdabh k'ogbok kw'odimbọhk k'ekpo py'ọfọr, ẹtzaanga.
\v 17 Ọtzọkha nnduma nnuma ọnang ọvaar Eglọn kwa Moab, kw'iwa ode ọnọng kw'ọbari ẹfa kpọng-kpọng.
\v 18 K'ogbe kw'Ehud okk'oyok nnduma ọnanga, oben anọng p'ira atzọhk nnduma nnuma bi, bẹ akpa nnam abhana.
\v 19 Yina, mada bẹ apyiri k'agbatza pa bẹ atzim atza abanga ọbaanga Gilgal, Ehud ọkhaam obe mẹ ọkpa nnam k'Eglọn, oben-ẹ bi, “Ọvaarnọng o, kaam ngaam ẹkkaabha cha ndubhama cha mbeni bi, mgbaakh-ọ.”
\p Mẹ wọ ofon, ọvaar Eglọn oben akhaan-nọng pẹ bi, “Bọng nang man ọphaangi!” Mando kwa bẹ abin afona.
\p 
\v 20 Mando kw'Ehud oreng okhebha Eglọn kẹ da owobh ẹwọr mancheni k'ẹnyọhng ch'ẹvaar-ttọhmma chẹ, oben bi, “Kaam dim ẹkkaabha ch'Ibinọkpaabyi bi, nchen-ọ e.” Mada ọvaarnọng obin kẹ da owobh ẹwọr,
\v 21 mando kw'Ehud otzim kwabọhk kwẹ ọtzọr ọkkangkkaang kw'ọkpa k'ogbok. Otzim-ẹ okhum ọvaarnọng k'ẹbhọhr.
\v 22 Kaambi da ọkkangkkaang ttara ibọkh-ọbọhk sẹ anwẹ-ẹ k'ẹbhọhr maa, abhọri pẹ ayin k'iyaan wọ, wa Ehud ọkkangkkaang nwa k'ọrọbh, mando kw'iyaak ibubh ọkkangkkaang nwa.
\v 23 Wa Ehud orenga oyin k'iyaan, ọtzọkha amma p'ẹmaanggọ ch'ẹnyọhng ọgbak.
\p 
\v 24 Mada Ehud okk'orenga ofona, atzọhmnọng p'ọvaarnọng avura atza are bi amma p'ẹmaanggọ ch'ẹnyọhng akk'agbakha, bẹ an-aben bi “Okheri maana ọtza k'ẹpannam k'ẹmaanggọ ch'ẹvaar-ttọhmma ẹtzaanga e.”
\v 25 Wa bẹ awobha atzik maa, eden ebhir. Yina, ọvaarnọng amma pa mmaanggọ kokwung. Bẹ atzọkha ọgbọkhọrọ akwunga amma. Wa bẹ an-are da itta kwabẹ ọkk'ọtta m'ibhokhi, ope.
\p 
\v 26 K'ogbe kwa bẹ am-awobha mẹ atzik, Ehud ọrọbh ofona. Wa oreng k'okhubha kw'agbatza pa bẹ agwa k'ọtza, ọrọbh ochina ka Seira.
\v 27 Mada opyiri kẹ, ogyi obukpọhng k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim. Wa Ehud otzima anọng p'Israẹl eden, p'areng ahakha k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho.
\p 
\v 28 Iwa oben bẹ bi, “Bọng dọn-m abẹ, kkeri Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi okk'anọng pa Moab p'ade attattaanga-nọng pabọng, ọtzọkha okhe bọng ka mbọk.” Mando kw'iwa bẹ atzọn-ẹ abẹ akhakha atza atzọkha okhubha kw'asi agbin-ogbin k'Ọraanga kwa Jọrdan kw'ochin ka Moab. Bẹ ọnọng manda wani ọbọhk katte ojekha.
\v 29 Wa m'ogbe nwuma, bẹ afhu anọng pa Moab p'apyiri nnọhna ẹrọbh obhiri nzen. Wa akkenggitza biphyir ọmaana afanọng biphyir, ọnọng kw'ọrọbhi ọnaanga kode.
\v 30 M'ewu nduma, wa anọng pa Moab an-awobha k'irekhirek kw'ẹfa ch'anọng p'Israẹl. Wa ẹkhọma ch'Israẹl ewobha k'ẹmẹm ka cho arọbh anna.
\s1 Shamgar ode osi-aponga kw'Israẹl
\p 
\v 31 Mada ogbe kw'Ehud ọkk'ọkwọbha, Shamgar kw'ode nnwa kw'Anat, obiro ode ọnọng kw'otzim ọbhaam-kkọhbhi ofhu anọng pa Philistiya p'apyiri ẹnọhna obhiri arọbh jobh. Wa kẹ Shamgar obiro ọkkaana anọng p'Israẹl.
\c 4
\s1 Debọra ode osi-aponga kw'Israẹl
\p 
\v 1 K'ogbe kw'Ehud ọkk'ọpa, wa anọng p'Israẹl abira asi ebibya k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi.
\v 2 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi otte bẹ ọbọhk ọnang Jabin, kw'ode ọvaarnọng kw'ẹkhọma cha Kenaan, ọdabh ẹvaar ka Hazọr. Wa Sisẹra ode oho kw'arim-egbong pẹ, oruk ka Haroshẹt-Hagoyim.
\v 3 Da iwa kẹ ọkhaam akpaar pa nnyanyaang mmindọr pa bẹ atzim akkonga asi, nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh azen, p'okk'otzima osi anọng p'Israẹl ọgbaan ka cho ẹrọbh. Wa anọng p'Israẹl abhom aror ẹkkaana k'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi.
\p 
\v 4 M'ogbe nwa, wa Debọra kw'ode osi-ẹjaakhi, obiro ode kwanọng kwa Lapidot wọ om-osi aponga p'anọng p'Israẹl.
\v 5 Wa om-owobha k'Oji kwa Debọra kw'obe k'ottem kwa Rama ọmaana Bẹtẹl, k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim osi aponga. Wa anọng p'Israẹl biphyir am-atza akhebh-ẹ kẹ bi, osi aponga pabẹ.
\v 6 Wa ọtzọhm bẹ ayeri Barak kw'ode nnwa kw'Abinoam kw'ofon Kadẹsh k'ẹkhọma cha Naphtali, oben-ẹ bi, “Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kw'Israẹl ọnang-ọ ẹfa bi: ‘Rọhng ka Naphtali ọmaana ka Zebulun, atza atzọkha ajinọng nnọhna ẹrọbh obhiri azen, atzima bẹ eden bọng avura k'egbegbeho cha Tabọr.
\v 7 Kaam ńdima Sisẹra kw'ode oho kw'arim-egbong pa Jabin eden, ọmaana akpaar pẹ pa nnyanyaang mmindọr, ttara arim-egbong pẹ ńchina k'Ọraanga kwa Kishọn, ńdọkha bẹ ńgọ-ọ ka mbọhk.’ ”
\p 
\v 8 Mẹ wọ ofon, Barak oben-ẹ bi, “Idikha kọ atzọn-m abẹ, kaam ńda-ọtza; yina, idikha an'aam abẹ atzọni, kaam kínda.”
\p 
\v 9 Debọra obhina bi, “K'odik-ọkka, kaam ndọn-ọ abẹ ọtzọn-ẹ. Yina, okhuri eden ch'am-asi m'odik nwa, echora kakhaama e, da Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ótte Sisẹra ọbọhk otte kwanọng, okhem-ẹ e.”
\v 10 Mando kwa Barak otzobh ajinọng pa Zebulun ọmaana pa Naphtali, anọng nnọhna ẹrọbh obhiri azen p'awobh k'irekhirek kw'ẹfa chẹ. Wa Debọra ọtzọn-ẹ abẹ.
\p 
\v 11 M'ogbe nwa, wa Heber kw'ofon Ken okk'obina oji ayok-afonava pa Ken, p'ade va pa va pa Hobab kw'iwa ode ọnyẹ kwa Mosẹs, ọtza ottima ikhira sẹ k'irekhirek kw'echi ch'ideden ka Zaananim ọbaanga Kadẹsh.
\p 
\v 12 K'ogbe kwa bẹ an-agbaakhi Sisẹra bi, Barak kw'ode nnwa kw'Abinoam okk'egbegbeho cha Tabọr ovura,
\v 13 Sisẹra ọtzọkha ajinọng pẹ biphyir okwu ọttara k'akpaar pẹ pa nnyanyaang mmindọr pa bẹ atzim akkonga asi, nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh azen otzobha. Ttẹwọr ka Haroshẹt-Hagoyim maa, atza apyiri k'Ọraanga kwa Kishọn.
\p 
\v 14 Mando kwa Debọra obeni Barak bi, “Kọ rọhng! Kkeri, k'ewu cha mayina, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi okk'Sisẹra ọtzọkha okhe ka mbọhk sa kọ Barak. Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọkk'ọ abẹ atzọna e” Wa Barak otzima ajinọng nnọhna ẹrọbh obhiri azen p'atzọn-ẹ abẹ, ovura k'egbegbeho cha Tabọr.
\v 15 Mada Barak oreng okwu, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi orenga k'ọkkangkkaang kwa Barak okhubh Sisẹra, ọmaana akpaar pẹ pa nnyanyaang mmindọr biphyir ttara arim-egbong pẹ maa, Sisẹra ọhakha k'ọkpaar kwẹ kwa nnyanyaang mmindọr, on-otzima mmo ọrọbh.
\p 
\v 16 Iwa Barak okhubh akpaar mba pa nnyanyaang mmindọr ọmaana arim-egbong maa, opyiri ka Haroshẹt-Hagoyim. Arim-egbong pa Sisẹra biphyir ape k'ọkkangkkaang, ojinọng manda wani korikhi.
\v 17 Wa Sisẹra otzima mmo ọrọbh maa, ọtza opyiri k'ikhira sa Jayẹl, kw'ode kwanọng kwa Heber kw'ofon Ken, okhuri da iwa Jabin kw'ode ọvaarnọng kwa Hazọr ọmaana ẹhọhmmọr cha Heber kw'ofon Ken akhaam echekhi ch'ẹmẹm.
\p 
\v 18 Iwa Jayẹl oyin k'iyaan ọtza okhebha Sisẹra oben-ẹ bi, “Itta kwaam kwu, dim k'ẹtzaanga. Tte oning-ọ ojor.” Mando kw'odimi k'ikhira sa Jayẹl, Jayẹl ọtzọkha ẹnọhmma-kpa obubh-ẹ.
\p 
\v 19 Sisẹra on-oben bi, “Ẹdọhngi ẹkk'aam ẹgwa e. Tzotzokhaan, nang-m asi ngwo.” Mando kwa Jayẹl ogwong ẹkpa ch'abasi cha bẹ atzim etzenkpa asi, okhaabha ọnang-ẹ ogwo obiro obubh-ẹ.
\p 
\v 20 Sisẹra oben Jayẹl bi, “Kọ be m'ekhiramma. Ọnọng manda wani okwu ọbọbh-ọ s'ọnọng owobh ma, bhin-ẹ bi, ‘Mma o.’ ”
\p 
\v 21 Yina, wa Jayẹl kw'ode kwanọng kwa Heber otzini obhin wani kw'ikhira ọmaana ẹtzabọhk, ọbẹkhi ọtza okhebha Sisẹra kẹ da ọkk'ẹ ọkhọhna oyima ọttaabha. Okhum-ẹ obhin nwuma k'ohobem ọmaana k'irek, ope.
\p 
\v 22 Mẹ ẹbaa mẹ, Barak kw'om-okhubh Sisẹra opyiri. Mando kwa Jayẹl oyini k'iyaan ọtza okhebh-ẹ, oben bi, “Kwu e, kaam ńdibh-ọ ọnọng kw'am-aror otzibh e.” Mando kwa Barak ọtzọn-ẹ abẹ odim k'ikhira, ọtza ore da Sisẹra on-oyim obukhi kẹ ttara obhin kw'okhum-ẹ k'ohobem.
\p 
\v 23 M'ewu nduma, anọng p'Israẹl are odem kw'Ibinọkpaabyi okhem ọvaar Jabin kwa Kenaan.
\v 24 Mando kw'anọng p'Israẹl achin ororo agaangi ayọhnga ọvaar Jabin kwa Kenaan maa, bẹ adim-ẹ.
\c 5
\s1 Ẹmọng ch'ekhema cha Debọra ọmaana Barak akkọhni
\p 
\v 1 Mada egbong ẹha m'ewu nduma, Debọra ọmaana Barak kw'ode nnwa kw'Abinoam akkọhni ẹmọng nda:
\q1 
\v 2 “K'ogbe kw'adeho ade atzim-eden k'Israẹl,
\q2 k'ogbe kw'anọng atte for sabẹ ọbọhk anang k'egbong,
\q2 anọng anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ẹtzọhnga!
\b
\q1 
\v 3 “Avaar o, bọng maanga odik nwa e!
\q2 Adabh o, bọng yonga itzọhng e!
\q1 Kaam e, kaam-ọkhaam wọ ńkkọhn ẹmọng nnang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi;
\q2 Kaam ńdima ọkkọhna ndọhnga Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kw'Israẹl.
\b
\q1 
\v 4 “O Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, mada abin ka mgbegbeho sa Seir,
\q2 mada abin k'ẹkhọma ch'Edom,
\q1 irerek inyengi, ọrọngkpakpa otzebh asi,
\q2 eboni ebire etzebh asi.
\q1 
\v 5 Mgbegbeho nnyengi k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kaambi cha Sinai dọ,
\q2 enyengi k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kw'Israẹl.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 “K'ogbe kwa Shamgar kw'ode nnwa kw'Anat,
\q2 ọmaana k'ogbe kwa Jayẹl, wa anọng arenga dọk kamatza;
\q2 wa anọng an-am-atza arenga ka ngọbhakhọbha-den.
\q1 
\v 7 Akkakkaama k'Israẹl dọk kade
\q2 maa, kaam Debọra ndọkha ẹfa,
\q2 nkkeri anọng p'Israẹl macha ọkka okkeri va.
\q1 
\v 8 Ibinọkpaabyi otzek adeho abhapẹ,
\q2 k'ogbe kw'egbong epyiri ka mbaakhamma s'odedenmon,
\q1 ọkhọhnkpa manda wani kaambi ọkhọhn f'ọnọng ore ka chen vọ, kode,
\q2 k'ottem kw'arim-egbong nnọhna arọbh azen k'Israẹl.
\q1 
\v 9 Ettem chaam ewobh ttara adeho p'Israẹl,
\q2 ewobh ttara anọng p'akher bi, atte for sabẹ ọbọhk k'ottem kw'anọng p'Israẹl.
\q2 Ẹtzọhnga ewobha ẹnang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi!
\b
\q1 
\v 10 “Bọbọng p'ayaari k'anyanyaang-wuri,
\q2 bọbọng p'awobh ẹwọr ka nnọhmakpa nkkakkasẹ,
\q2 ttara ayok p'areng ka mmo, bọng chibhi odik
\v 11 okhuri ẹmọng ch'akkọhni-ẹmọng akkọhni ka nsipe.
\q2 Bẹ agbaakhi ngema s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi,
\q2 bẹ agbaak ngema sa ndor-otzor s'anọng pẹ p'ibhon s'Israẹl.
\b
\q1 “Anọng p'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi,
\q2 abin ahakha ka mbaakhamma s'odedenmon, aben bi,
\q1 
\v 12 ‘Bina k'ẹrọng, bina k'ẹrọng, Debọra!
\q2 Bina k'ẹrọng, bina k'ẹrọng, atzima man akkọhn ẹmọng ch'ekhema!
\q1 Barak, bina k'ẹrọng!
\q2 atzọkha attattaanga-nọng pọ p'abọk k'ẹmmọri, o nnwa kwa Abinoam.’
\b
\q1 
\v 13 “Adeho p'arikhi ahakha akwu;
\q2 anọng p'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ahakha akwu akhebh-m bi, mọtza orima afanọng abẹ.
\q1 
\v 14 Ayok bani afon k'ẹkhọma ch'Ephraim, p'immaanabe sabẹ ide Amalẹk;
\q2 anọng pa Bẹnjamin awobha k'ottem kw'anọng p'atzọn-ọ abẹ.
\q1 Adeho p'arim-egbong afona ka Makir,
\q2 anọng p'atzim ẹvaar-chi ch'odeho kw'arim-egbong afona ka Zebulun.
\q1 
\v 15 Wa adeho p'Isaaka awobha ttara Debọra;
\q2 k'odik-ọkka Isaaka owobh ttara Barak,
\q2 kw'odeho kwẹ ọtzọhmi akhubh-ẹ apyiri k'ittolim.
\q1 Yina, ka ngọma sa Reubẹn achibhi ahaabhi bẹ kpọng.
\q1 
\v 16 Bọng asi yan awobha k'ottem kw'avu-kwuri bi,
\q2 bọng abhaanga eyeri ch'arukhimaan?
\q1 ka ngọma sa Reubẹn achibhi ahaabhi bẹ kpọng.
\q1 
\v 17 Anọng pa Gilead awobh ka Jọrdan okhubha.
\q2 Anọng pa Dan asi yan awobha k'ọraanga ọkhaan-ọkhaan o?
\q1 Anọng p'Ashẹr akpong k'ẹraangamma,
\q2 awobha ka bẹ k'ẹkha.
\q1 
\v 18 Anọng pa Zebulun akhe akpen pabẹ ka dama-dama;
\q2 mando kw'anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Naphtali abira akhe akpen pabẹ ka dama-dama, ka mgbongdam.
\b
\q1 
\v 19 “Avaar akwu arima erima,
\q2 avaar pa Kenaan arima erima;
\q1 abaanga ngekha sa Mẹgido, ka Taanak,
\q2 yina, bẹ silva manda wani katzọk.
\q1 
\v 20 Ndodori nwobh k'ọrọngkpakpa nnima erima,
\q2 odem nwa kwa sẹ nneng k'ọrọngkpakpa,
\q2 sẹ nnima Sisẹra abẹ.
\q1 
\v 21 Ebhobh ch'ọraanga kwa Kishọn ẹchọri bẹ etzima efona,
\q2 ebukhaya ch'ọraanga kwa Kishọn ebubha bẹ, ẹchọri bẹ biphyir-phyir etzima efona.
\q2 Ọgbagba kwaam o, china ororo agaangi for!
\b
\q1 
\v 22 Ndọkhi sa nnyanyaang nnimi irerek,
\q2 nnyanyaang sa Sisẹra s'ẹfa ndukha-odukha.
\q1 
\v 23 Oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oben bi, ‘Opyibh-opyibh ọnang Meroz.’
\q2 ‘Opyibh-opyibh ọnang anọng pa Meroz itzama-itzama,
\q1 okhuri da iwa bẹ ani Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi attar arima abaSisẹra abẹ,
\q2 bẹ Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi kattar arima attattaanganọng p'ẹfa abẹ.’
\b
\q1 
\v 24 “Echora cha Jayẹl ẹbari ẹyọhnga ch'ayokhi-panọng,
\q2 Jayẹl kw'ode kwanọng kwa Heber kw'ofon Ken,
\q2 echora chẹ ẹbari ẹyọhnga cha panọng mach'ẹ, p'abira aruk k'okhira.
\q1 
\v 25 Sisẹra ophyem-ẹ asi, Jayẹl ọnang-ẹ abasi;
\q2 otzima ọgwasi kw'avaar ọnang-ẹ abasi p'akk'amaanga.
\q1 
\v 26 Jayẹl onemi ọbọhk ọtzọkha obhing,
\q2 otzima odimbọhk otzini ọtzọhmttọhk mach'ẹtzabọhk,
\q1 otzima okhum Sisẹra, otzukh-ẹ eho,
\q2 ommun-ẹ k'ohobem, otzukh-ẹ \it bi biribiri\it*.
\q1 
\v 27 Sisẹra obikhi otto,
\q2 oyima Jayẹl ma ndọkhi;
\q1 otto oyima Jayẹl ma ndọkhi;
\q2 okponga mẹ da otto ope.
\b
\q1 
\v 28 “Ọkka kwa Sisẹra orenga k'ọphapha-mma omyinga,
\q2 owobha k'ọphapha-mma nnam-annam obhom;
\q1 ‘Okhuri yan kw'ọkpaar kwẹ kwa nnyanyaang mmindọr okpeni okhukhuna manda o?
\q2 Abirikum p'akpaar pẹ pa nnyanyaang mmindor an-akpeni yan ma o?’
\q1 
\v 29 Oyokh-omina wani kwẹ kw'orong atzim obhin-ẹ bi,
\q2 k'odik-ọkka, om-obiro oben for sẹ bi,
\q1 
\v 30 ‘Nne bi, bẹ am-atzọkha ekpo am-abira achi ọgbọm e,
\q1 ajinọng am-atzọk panọng kẹ e,
\q1 bẹ am-achi ọgbọm f'anọhma-baba ọkkakka anang Sisẹra,
\q2 anọhma-baba akkakka afa,
\q2 idik nna biphyir ide ọgbọm.’
\b
\q1 
\v 31 “O Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, tte attattaanganọng pọ biphyir adimi!
\q2 Yina, tte anọng p'adaakhi amaani mach'ekpekhira,
\q2 k'ogbe kwa chẹ eyini ttara ẹfa.”
\p Mando kw'iwa ẹkhọma nda ẹkhaam odidiri ka cho arọbh afa.
\c 6
\s1 Anọng pa Midiyan ahokhi anọng p'Israẹl k'ihem
\p 
\v 1 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl abira asi itzama k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, Ibinọkpaabyi otte bẹ ọbọhk ọnang anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Midiyan, ka cho azenamfa.
\v 2 Da iwa anọng pa Midiyan akhaam ẹfa ayọhnga anọng p'Israẹl, anọng p'Israẹl afona atza asi orukhabe fabẹ ka mgbegbeho ebira, ọmaana k'atzakpamma ttara k'ochubhabe.
\v 3 Ogbe kpenamkpen kw'anọng p'Israẹl ayaabh iwoni sabẹ, anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Midiyan, ọmaana ch'Amalẹk ttara anọng pa ngọma s'irukhi k'okhubha kw'ewuchen em-eyin, am-afona atza arima anọng p'Israẹl abẹ.
\v 4 Anọng mba am-abhing mẹ bẹ akhibhi iwoni maa, apyiri Gaza bẹ anọng p'Israẹl otzirattọhk manda vani f'ode orukhimaan, obiro ode ẹbhaam ttara ẹnyanyaang, karikhi.
\v 5 Wa bẹ abin ttara etzirakpo pyabẹ, omaana okhira fabẹ mach'ọhaabh f'agwuribhebhe. Wa bẹ ajinọng ọmaana akamẹl pabẹ kafha abhik; bẹ abọkha ẹkhọma nda bẹ abira akhibhi ọttọhk kpenamkpen.
\v 6 Anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Midiyan ahok anọng p'Israẹl k'ihem s'okwo maa, anọng p'Israẹl abhom ẹkkaana anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi.
\p 
\v 7 K'ogbe kw'anọng p'Israẹl abhomi ẹkkaana anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, okhuri k'ihem s'anọng pa Midiyan ahokhi bẹ,
\v 8 ọtzọhm ọsẹjaakhi ọnang bẹ, kw'obeni bi, “Ma wọ ode odik kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kw'Israẹl obeni bi: kaam ndim bọng mbina k'Ijip k'ẹkhọma nduma cha bọng awobh k'ihem.
\v 9 Kaam nnọbh bọng ka mbọhk s'anọng p'Ijip, ọmaana ka mbọhk s'anọng biphyir p'ahokhi bọng k'ihem, ngwubh bẹ k'itzitzikha sabọng, mbiri ndọkha irerek sabẹ nnang bọng.
\v 10 Mben bọng bi, ‘Kaam wọ nde Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kwabọng; bọng ikha s'anọng p'Amọr pa bọng arukhi k'irerek sabẹ kàkpobha.’ Yina, bọng itzọhng kayong anang-m.”
\p 
\v 11 Iwa ewu dani, oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ofona kẹ okwu k'obhon kw'Ọphra, ọtza owobha ẹwọr k'irekhirek kw'echi ch'ideden cha oak ch'ede echi cha Joash kw'ofon Abiez, kẹ da nnwa kwẹ Gideọn owobh om-okhok abọkpa, k'ibe sa bẹ am-amyana achiduk, ifha anọng pa Midiyan aningi bẹ are.
\v 12 Mada oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oyini Gideọn abẹ, oben bi, “Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi owobh kẹ ttar-ọ, kọ orim-egbong kw'ideden.”
\p 
\v 13 Yina, Gideọn obhina bi, “Idikha Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi owobh kẹ ttara man, okhuri yan kw'idik nna biphyir itto ikhebha man o? Ikkokkoni-dik sẹ biphyir ki s'ab'otte paman am-agbaak man okhuri kẹ, aben bi, ‘Wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi man kotzim obina k'Ijip o?’ Yina, madeden Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi okk'nnam ọkpa ọbọra man, obiro ọtzọkha man okhe ka mbọhk s'anọng pa Midiyan.”
\p 
\v 14 Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọbhakhi okker-ẹ, oben bi, “Kọ tzima ẹfa ch'akhaam arọhng atza akkaana anọng p'Israẹl, ka mbọhk s'anọng pa Midiyan. Kaam ọkhaam ma for saam wọ ndọhm-ọ.”
\p 
\v 15 Yina, Gideọn ọbọbh bi, “Itta, yan kwa kaam mfha nkkaana anọng p'Israẹl o? Efonamma chaam dọ ẹkhar ọtzam k'ẹkhọma cha Manasẹ. Kaam wọ mbiri ngara ọtzam k'ẹhọhmmọr ch'otte kwaam.”
\p 
\v 16 Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi obhina bi, “Kaam ńwobha ttar-ọ, kọ ábira afhu anọng pa Midiyan biphyir-phyir maana afhu ọnọng wani.”
\p 
\v 17 Gideọn on-obhina bi, “Idikha madeden kaam nkk'ọphyaam ndọkha k'itzitzikha sọ, kọ si ẹjaakhi anang-m ifha nnonga bi, k'odik-ọkka kọ wọ am-agbaakh-m atzim.
\v 18 Tzotzokhaan, kọ kafona maa, kaam mkpa nnam ttara ẹnanga chaam, nkwu nji chẹ m'itzitzikha sọ.”
\p Mẹ wọ, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọben bi, “Kaam nwobha-owobha ndik maa, akhuna.”
\p 
\v 19 Mando kwa Gideọn ofon ọtza ọtzọkha ovu-nwa ofhu otzima osi ọchattọhk, obiro ọtzọkha abubuma k'ọgbanggbang otzima osi brẹd kwa bẹ ani yist akhe. Ọtzọkha ọchattọhk mva f'okhe k'ikhiriba, ọmaana etzen nda ch'ewobh k'irọhkha otzima ọtza ober-ẹ m'echirin cha oak.
\p 
\v 20 Oreng-eden kw'Ibinọkpaabyi oben-ẹ bi, “Tzini etzen nda ọmaana brẹd nwa kwa bẹ ani yist akhe, anana pyẹ m'itzakpa nna, ayaanga ẹbọhnga nda mẹ.” Wa Gideọn osi mando.
\v 21 Oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi otzima ironẹmma s'ochikhura kw'otzim k'ọbọhk kwẹ, ọttọhmi etzen nda ọmaana brẹd nwa kwa bẹ ani yist akhe. Ekpon eyin m'ẹtzakpa nda echi etzen nda ọmaana brẹd. Mando kw'oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọdakhi odimi.
\v 22 Mada Gideọn on-orong bi, oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi wọ, ọkpẹbh oben bi, “O Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi kw'ọyọhng! Kaam nkk'orenga-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, itzitzikha ttara itzitzikha nna!”
\p 
\v 23 Yina, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oben-ẹ bi, “Odidiri owobha ttar-ọ! Oning-ọ ojor, Kọ kápe.”
\p 
\v 24 Mẹ wọ ofon, Gideọn osi ijafọhnibe mẹ, ọnang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, oyeri sẹ Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi wọ ode ẹmẹm. Ma pyiri k'ewu cha mayina ijafọhnibe nna, ibe k'obhon kw'Ọphra k'ẹkhọma ch'Abiez.
\p 
\v 25 M'erungiwu nduma dani Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oben Gideọn bi, “Tzọkha ẹbhaam-dim ch'ẹkhaam ẹfa ch'ettong mfa k'etzirakpo py'atte, ch'ede cho azenamfa. Atzima anyuni ijafọhnibe nna s'atte om-owobha okpobha Baal abira akpaara mkpọmmachi s'Ashẹra sa mbe k'ẹbhabhaanga chẹ.
\v 26 Asi ijafọhnibe ikkakkasẹ k'egbegbeho ebira ttara atza, anang kaam Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kwa nde Ibinọkpaabyi kwọ. Tzima mkpọmmachi nna s'Ashẹra s'akpaar, ọmaana ẹbhaam-dim nda ch'ettong mfa asi ẹjafọhni ẹkwọmichẹ.”
\p 
\v 27 Mando wọ kwa Gideọn ọtzọk atzọhmnọng pẹ jobh, ofona ọtza osi mach'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọgbaakh-ẹ. Yina, okhuri ojora f'ọkhaam ọmaana anọng pẹ ttara f'ajinọng p'obhon kw'Ọphra, osi ijafọhnibe nna k'erungi, kw'ira osi sẹ k'ẹya.
\p 
\v 28 K'ekpebha mada ajinọng p'obhon nwa aphyọbh, bẹ an-are bi, ijafọhnibe sa Baal ikk'ikhibhi, ẹkpọmmachi ch'Ashẹra ch'ebe m'ẹbhabhaanga ebire ẹkpaara, bẹ abira atzima ẹbhaam-dim nda ch'ettong mfa asi ẹjafọhni, m'ijafọhnibẹ nna ibhasẹ.
\p 
\v 29 Bẹ abhakhi abọbh ayok bi, “Anyi wọ osi odik nwa?”
\p Mada bẹ atzọk ogbe adọn kwẹ, bẹ agbaak bẹ bi, “Gideọn kw'ode nnwa kwa Joash wọ osi kwẹ.”
\p 
\v 30 Mando wọ kw'ajinọng p'obhon nwa afon atza aben Joash bi, “Tzima nnwa kwọ kw'ijinọng ayin ka. Kẹ ọkhaambi ope, okhuri bi, kẹ okk'ijafọhnibe sa Baal ọvọhkhi obiro ọkpaara ẹkpọmmachi ch'Ashẹra ch'ebe ẹbaanga sẹ.”
\p 
\v 31 Yina, Joash obhina ọnọngẹya haabha nwa kw'ettem ekk'epyibha kw'ọkhọr-ẹ okhe k'ottem bi, “Na bọng arima erima nda k'eho cha Baal o? Bọng am-akhong bi, akkaan-ẹ? Ọnọng manda wani kw'orim erima k'eho cha Baal bẹ akhaambi afhẹ-ẹ k'ekpebha! Idikha Baal ọkhaam ẹfa k'odik-ọkka, tte orima erima cha for sẹ k'ogbe kw'ọnọng ọvọhkhi ijafọhnibe sẹ.”
\v 32 Mẹ wọ ofon m'ewu nduma bẹ an-ayeri Gideọn “Jerub-Baal,” aben bi, “Tte Baal orima erima ttar-ẹ,” okhuri da ọvọhkhi ijafọhnibe sa Baal.
\p 
\v 33 M'ogbe nwa, wa ẹkhọma cha Midiyan, ọmaana ch'Amalẹk ttara ngọma ndọdọk s'irukhi k'okhubha kw'ewuchen em-eyin, bẹ abhuna ẹfa njekha ọraanga kwa Jọrdan nda mming ka ittolim sa Jẹzrẹl.
\v 34 Mando kw'egwugwuma ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ẹhak ẹnwa Gideọn, ogyi obukpọhng otzima oyeri anọng p'Abiez bi, bẹ atzọn-ẹ abẹ.
\v 35 Ọtzọhm akkaabh-nkkaabha k'ẹkhọma cha Manasẹ biphyir bi, bẹ atzima egbongkpo akwu, obiro ọtzọhm ochena ẹkhọma ch'Ashẹr, ọmaana cha Zebulun ttara cha Naphtali, ifha bẹ-bẹ dọk abira avura akhebha bẹ kẹ.
\p 
\v 36 Gideọn e, oben Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi bi, “Idikha ọdaakh-ọ bi, arenga ka kaam ka mbọhk akkaana anọng p'Israẹl mach'akk'achekhi,
\v 37 kkere e, kaam ńdọkha ngwugwuma nnana m'ibe sa bẹ am-awobha agwuma abọkpamọma. Idikha abonisi atzebhi ma ngwugwuma nna sẹ-sẹ bẹ k'irerek katzebhi, mẹ wọ kwa kaam ńdima nnonga bi, kọ arenga-orenga ka mbọhk saam akkaana anọng p'Israẹl, mach'agbaakhi.”
\v 38 Manda wọ kwa kwẹ ode. Gideọn ọphyọbha k'ekpekpebha k'ewu ch'ekhobh; ọmyana ngwugwuma nnuma asi ayin p'afhu ogbobhi-mbọhk.
\p 
\v 39 Mẹ wọ e, Gideọn oben Ibinọkpaabyi bi, “Oning-ọ ọdọkhi ttara kaam. Tte kaam mbiri mphyem ogbe nwa wani. Tte-m ọbọhk m'ogbe nwa mbiri nsi eyoma ttara ngwugwuma nna. M'ogbe nwa, kọ si ngwugwuma nna ngwu, abonisi abubha irerek.”
\v 40 M'erungiwu nduma, Ibinọkpaabyi osi mando. Ngwugwuma sẹ-sẹ ngwu; abonisi abubha irerek biphyir.
\c 7
\s1 Gideọn okhem anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Midiyan
\p 
\v 1 Iwa k'ekpebhawu dani, Jerub-Baal (kw'ode Gideọn) ọmaana ajinọng pẹ biphyir abhing k'okhekhaho kwa Harọd. Wa ibhingabe s'anọng pa Midiyan iwobh k'ebira-ebira kw'ittolim s'ibaang egbegbeho cha More.
\v 2 Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oben Gideọn bi, “Ajinọng p'akhaam ahaabhi kpọng bi, kaam ndọkha anọng pa Midiyan nge bẹ ka mbọhk. Oni mando ode, anọng p'Israẹl an-asi ẹmma bi, ‘Ẹfa chaman ekk'man ẹkkaana e.’
\v 3 Na si ẹjaakhi anang arim-egbong bi, ‘Tte ọnọng kpenamkpen kw'ojor-ẹ ojora obina k'egbegbeho cha Gilead ọkpa nnam.’ ” Mando kw'ajinọng nnọhna arọbh afa obhiri chi, akpa nnam abhana, on-omunga ajinọng nnọhna ẹrọbh obhiri nzen.
\p 
\v 4 Yina, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oben Gideọn bi, “Ajinọng mba atzima ahaabhi kpọng e. Tzima bẹ ahakha k'ekhekha, ifha nyoma bẹ nnang-ọ. Idikha mbeni bi, ‘Oyok nwa wọ ọ́tzọn-ọ abẹ,’ kẹ wọ ọ́tzọn-ọ abẹ; yina, idikha mbeni bi, ‘Oyok nwa kọ abẹ kọ́tzọn,’ kọ abẹ kọ́tzọn.”
\p 
\v 5 Mando kwa Gideọn otzim ajinọng mba ọhakha k'ekhekha. Mẹ wọ kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oben-ẹ bi, “K'ottem kw'anọng p'attim ndudungi agwo asi, kọ tzekha anọng p'atzim ẹdaak agberi asi, mach'ẹpfa ẹttaakhi asi.”
\v 6 Wa ajinọng arọbh chi bọ atzim mbọhk akhaabha asi agwo. Ajinọng mbonggo biphyir attima ndudungi agwo.
\p 
\v 7 Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oben Gideọn bi, “Ajinọng mbuma arọbh chi p'atzim mbọhk akhaabha asi agwo, bọ pa kaam ńnenga mẹ ńkkaan-ọ, ḿbiri ndọkha anọng pa Midiyan ńge bọng ka mbọhk. Tte ajinọng mbonggo biphyir akpa nnam, ọnọng-ọnọng k'ikhira sẹ.”
\v 8 Mando wọ kwa Gideọn ọtzọhmi anọng mbonggo biphyir p'Israẹl bẹ akpa nnam k'okhira fabẹ, yina, wa ohok ajinọng mba arọbh chi, p'atzọk agbere ọmaana abukpọhng p'anọng mbonggo p'afon-ofona.
\p M'ogbe nwa wa ibhingabe s'anọng pa Midiyan iwobh k'ittolim, k'irekhirek kwa Gideọn.
\v 9 M'erungi nduma Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oben Gideọn bi, “Bina ahakha atza arima anọng pa Midiyan abẹ k'ibhingabe sabẹ, okhuri bi, kaam ńdọkha bẹ ọ́tzọkha ngọ-ọ ka mbọhk.
\v 10 Idikha ojora ọsọ-ọ bi, atza arima bẹ abẹ, hakha k'ibhingabe ttara ọtzọhmnọng kwọ Pura,
\v 11 ayonga itzọhng abhaanga odik kwa bẹ am-agbaak. Mẹ wọ kw'abar ettem bi, atza arima anọng mba abẹ k'ibhingabe sabẹ.” Mẹ wọ e, kẹ ọmaana ọtzọhmnọng kwẹ Pura ahakha k'iyaan s'ibhingabe.
\v 12 Ode ch'anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Midiyan, ọmaana anọng p'ẹkhọma ch'Amalẹk ttara anọng pa ngọma sa nnukhi k'okhubha kwa ewuchen em-eyin akk'azobha k'ọhaabh mach'agwuribhebhe k'ittolim. Akamẹl pabẹ abira ahaabh mach'oyeyeng kw'ọraanga kw'ọnọng oni ov-obhik.
\p 
\v 13 Mando kwa Gideọn otzor-otzor ọtza opyiri m'ogbe nwuma kw'ojinọng wani ọm-ọgbaak oyok idachen s'ọttaar bi, “Kaam nttaar idachen, nne da brẹd kw'ode iriring kwa bẹ atzim barli asi, om-otto ogina maa, odim k'ibhingabe s'anọng pa Midiyan. Otzima ẹfa nduma ọtza ọtzọhbh k'ikhira, ihọbhi itto ikhubha.”
\p 
\v 14 Mẹ wọ ofon, oyok-odikkobh kwẹ obhina bi, “Odem ọdọdọk kode, oyongi bi, ọkkangkkaang kwa Gideọn kw'ode nnwa kwa Joash, kw'ofon Israẹl wọ e. Ibinọkpaabyi okk'anọng pa Midiyan, ọmaana ibhingabe sabẹ biphyir ọtzọkha ọkhẹ-ẹ ka mbọhk.”
\p 
\v 15 K'ogbe kwa Gideọn ọbhaang idachen nna ttara ẹjaakhi chẹ, ọrakha ọnang Ibinọkpaabyi ikpokpobha. Ọkpa nnam ọbhana k'ibhingabe s'anọng p'Israẹl, oben bẹ bi, “Bọng bina e! Kkeri Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi okk'anọng pa Midiyan, ọmaana ibhingabe sabẹ ọtzọkha okhe bọng ka mbọhk e.”
\v 16 Ọbhaangi ajinọng mba arọbh chi ka ngaan nttaan, ọtzọkha abukpọhng, ọmaana agbere p'ọttọhk on-ode okhe bẹ biphyir ka mbọhk, ttara okhebh f'oyeni k'agbere mba ẹtzaanga.
\p 
\v 17 Oben bẹ bi, “Bọng kker-m mo o, bọng dor-m ma ndọkhi. Mada mpyiri m'ibhingabe ọkhaan-ọkhaan, odik kpenamkpen kwa nsi, bọng si mando.
\v 18 Mada kaam ttara anọng biphyir p'awobh ttar-m mogyi abukpọhng paman, mando kwa bọng biphyir p'awobh akhọri ibhingabe, agyi abukpọhng pabọng abira awuri ẹmọng aben bi, ‘Ekhema ede ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, ọmaana cha Gideọn.’ ”
\p 
\v 19 Mando kwa Gideọn ọmaana ajinọng arọbh azen p'awobh ttar-ẹ atza apyiri k'ibhingabe s'anọng mba ọkhaan-ọkhaan, k'ogbe kwa bẹ akk'akkeribe abhona. Bẹ agyi abukpọhng pabẹ, abira avọhkhi agbere mbuma pa bẹ atzim ka mbọhk.
\v 20 Ngaan nna nttaan ngyi abukpọhng mbiri mvọhkhi agbere. Ọnọng-ọnọng otzima ikhebh ka kwabọhk, ọmaana obukpọhng k'odimbọhk, ọnọng-ọnọng owuri ẹmọng, oben bi, “Bọng nima erima nda ttara akkangkkaang pabọng anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ttara Gideọn!”
\v 21 Ojinọng kpenamkpen obe k'ibe sẹ, bẹ akhọri ibhingabe nna, anọng pa Midiyan biphyir am-abhom arọbh.
\p 
\v 22 Mada abukpọhng mba arọbh chi agyi, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọgara ajinọng pa Midiyan biphyir bẹ abhakhi atzima akkangkkaang pabẹ arima for sabẹ abẹ. Arim-egbong mba arọbh achina ka Bet-Shita da achin ka Zerera maa, atza apyiri k'enem cha Abẹl-Mẹhola ọbaanga Tabat.
\v 23 Anọng p'Israẹl p'afon k'ẹkhọma cha Naphtali, ọmaana ch'Ashẹr, ọmaana ẹkhọma cha Manasẹ biphyir ayin k'iyaan akhubh anọng pa Midiyan.
\v 24 Wa Gideọn ọtzọhm akkaabh-nkkaabha m'akhọra obhon kw'egbegbeho kw'Ephraim, oben bi, “Bọng hakha akwu arima anọng pa Midiyan abẹ, bọng abira akpa bẹ eden k'Ọraanga kwa Jọrdan maa, apyiri ka Bet-Bara.”
\p Mando wọ kw'ajinọng p'ẹkhọma ch'Ephraim biphyir afon atza akpa bẹ eden k'Ọraanga kwa Jọrdan maa, apyiri ka Bet-Bara.
\v 25 Iwa bẹ abira abọkha adeho afa p'anọng pa Midiyan, p'ade Oreb, ọmaana Zeeb. Bẹ afhu Oreb k'itzakpa s'Oreb, bẹ afhu Zeeb k'ibe sa bẹ am-amyana achiduk s'iwobh ka Zeeb. Wa bẹ akhubh anọng pa Midiyan bẹ atzima eho ch'Oreb, ọmaana cha Zeeb achena Gideọn, kw'owobh ka Jọrdan ọkhaan-ọkhaan.
\c 8
\s1 Zeba ọmaana Zalmuna
\p 
\v 1 Iwa anọng p'Ephraim abọbh Gideọn bi, “Osi yan asi man manda? Osi yan kw'ani man ayeri mọtzọn-ọ abẹ ọtza orima anọng pa Midiyan abẹ o?” Ọdọkhi bẹ itzama-itzama atzima atzor-ẹ.
\p 
\v 2 Yina, obhina bẹ bi, “Mbọng fa kaam nkk'nsa f'ode ebenga-mbọhk ka fa bọng akk'asa? Ichora sa bọng asi k'iwoni sa grep s'Ephraim, k'ijibhi iyọhnga ipha k'obungi s'owoni kwa grep kw'Abiezer o?
\v 3 Ibinọkpaabyi ọkk'Oreb, ọmaana Zeeb p'ade adeho p'anọng pa Midiyan ọtzọkha, okhe bọng ka mbọhk. Mbọng fa kaam nsi ma f'ọbari ọyọhnga fa kọ aso o?” Okhuri ebhina ch'ọnangi bẹ, idọdọkhi sa bẹ akhaam ttar-ẹ ihakha.
\p 
\v 4 Chibhi da Gideọn ọmaana ajinọng pẹ arọbh chi ọkhọhni bẹ, bẹ achina ororo akhubh anọng pa Midiyan maa, atza apyiri Jọrdan abira ajekha k'okhubha.
\v 5 Wa oben anọng pa Sukọt bi, “Bọng nang arim-egbong paam brẹd; kkeri okwo okk'bẹ ọkhaama, da kaam nchin ororo ngwubh Zeba ọmaana Zalmuna, p'ade avaarnọng pa Midiyan.”
\p 
\v 6 Yina, akhaan-nọng pa Sukọt aben bi, “Okhuri yan kwa mọnang arim-egbong pọ brẹd, k'ogbe kw'ani Zeba ọmaana Zalmuna atzim abọkha?”
\p 
\v 7 Mẹ wọ ofon, Gideọn obhina bi, “Idikha ode mando, k'ogbe kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọkk'aam Zeba, ọmaana Zalmuna ọkha ka mbọhk, kaam ńdima afhodima ọmaana akkaangi p'ameni k'ibe s'anọng an-arukhi, ńjaakhi ayaara pabọng k'abir-ibiri.”
\b
\p 
\v 8 Obina mẹ ochina ka Pẹniyẹl, ọtza ophyem odik nwuma wani. Yina, ajinọng p'obhon nwa abira anang bẹ ebhina nduma dani ch'ajinọng pa Sukọt akk'ananga.
\v 9 Mẹ wọ ofon, oben ajinọng pa Pẹniyẹl bi, “Mada ngwuna ttara ekhema, ńgibhi ibe nna s'akker-obhon am-awobha akkeri obhon.”
\p 
\v 10 Iwa Zeba ọmaana Zalmuna awobh ka Karkọr ttara arim-egbong p'apyiri ajinọng nnọhna ẹrọbh obhiri chi obhiri mfa obhiri arọbh jobh. Wa arim-egbong biphyir p'arikhi ka ngọma s'okhubha kw'ewuchen em-eyin bọ mẹ; da arim-egbong nnọhna arọbh chi p'atzim akkangkkaang akk'apa.
\v 11 Wa Gideọn orenga k'ọkkadeden kw'akker-etzirakpo p'arukhi k'okhira k'okhubha kw'ewuchen em-eyin ka Noba ọmaana ka Jogbeha, ọtza orima arim-egbong abẹ, k'ogbe kwa bẹ ani chen ahokhi.
\v 12 Mando kwa Zeba, ọmaana Zalmuna p'ade avaar afa pa Midiyan, arọbhi. Yina, Gideọn okhubh bẹ maa, ọbọkha bẹ, obiro okhe arim-egbong p'anọng mba biphyir k'ojora.
\p 
\v 13 Iwa Gideọn kw'ode nnwa kwa Joash ofona kẹ da orim egbong orenga k'Ọkkadeden kwa Heres, okhuna.
\v 14 Ọbọkha odikkobh wani kw'ofon Sukọt, ọdọhn-ẹ, odikkobh nwa e, ọkkẹr che p'akhaannọng pa Sukọt anọng arọbh attaan obhiri chi obhiri afa p'ade adedennọng p'obhon nwa, ọnang-ẹ.
\v 15 Mando kwa Gideọn ofon ọtza okhebha ajinọng pa Sukọt oben bẹ bi, “Bọng kkeri Zeba, ọmaana Zalmuna ma pa bọng areng abẹ am-alukh-m, aben bi, ‘Zeba ọmaana Zalmuna kho o? Kayan kwa mọnang ajinọng pọ p'ọkk'ọkhọhna brẹd o?’ ”
\v 16 Otzima adedennọng p'obhon nwa osi ẹkhọhkha ọnang anọng pa Sukọt, da otzim afhodima ọmaana akkaangi p'ameni k'ibe s'anọng an-arukhi ọnang bẹ ọmmamma.
\v 17 Wa obiro ọvọhkhi ibe s'akker-obhon am-awobha akkeri obhon kwa Pẹniyẹl, obiro ofhu ajinọng p'obhon nwa.
\p 
\v 18 Mẹ wọ, ọbọbh Zeba, ọmaana Zalmuna bi, “Bọng ajinọng dema pa bọng afhu ka Tabọr?”
\p Ajinọng mba abhina bi, “Ajinọng mach'ọ e, kpenamkpen otzim ebhora ch'ọvaar nnwa e.”
\p 
\v 19 Gideọn obhina bi, “Ajinọng mbuma ade vọkka paam e, bẹ ade va p'ijinọng p'ọkka kwaam. Odem nwa kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi orukhi akpen, ira bọng atte bẹ ọbọhk bẹ aruk akpen, kaam bọng kimfhu.”
\v 20 Ọbhakhi okkeri nnwa kwẹ Jeter kw'ọkk'ọkkọri, oben-ẹ bi, “Fhu bẹ!” Yina, Jeter ọkkaangkkaang kwẹ kọtzọri, okhuri da ode odikkobh obiro ojor-ẹ ojora.
\p 
\v 21 Mẹ wọ e, Zeba, ọmaana Zalmuna an-aben bi, “Kọ ọkhaam renga-mmo asi odik nwa. ‘Ojinọng bẹ arong-ẹ k'ẹfa chẹ e.’ ” Mando kwa Gideọn oreng ochina k'itzitzikha ofhu bẹ, ọtzọkha edokhakpo pya bẹ atzim akhaara akamẹl pabẹ k'ẹdọhngi.
\s1 Ẹphọd cha Gideọn
\p 
\v 22 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl aben Gideọn bi, “Na dabh man; kọ ọmaana nnwa kwọ kw'ijinọng, ọmaana nnwa mmona kwọ kw'ijinọng, okhuri bi, kọ akk'man akkaana arọbha man ka mbọhk s'anọng pa Midiyan.”
\p 
\v 23 Yina, Gideọn oben bẹ bi, “Kaam bọng kindabh, nnwa kwaam bọng kobiro ọdabh. Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi wọ ọdabh bọng.”
\v 24 Obiro oben bi, “Kaam ngaam ephyema dani, nnori bi, ọnọng-ọnọng ọnang-m ọttọhk f'itzọhng k'ekkema cha bọng achi ọgbọm.” (Iwa ode ẹmmaana ch'anọng p'Ishmayẹl bi, bẹ am-akhe ekpo py'itzọhng pya gol.)
\p 
\v 25 Bẹ abhina bi, “Ettem ẹdaam man bi, mọnang-ọ pyẹ.” Mando kwa bẹ atzọk ẹnọhmakpa aruri, ọnọng-ọnọng ọrọbha ọttọhk f'itzọhng ka ekkema chẹ ch'ọgbọm ọbhari mẹ.
\v 26 Wa ẹdọhbh ch'ekpo py'itzọhng mbya pya gol py'ọbọbhi bẹ, epyiri ashẹkẹl nnọhna nna obhiri ẹrọbh obhiri nzen, arọbh ẹdọhbh ch'edokhakpo, omaana ẹdọhbh ch'ekpo py'ẹdọhngi ttara ch'ewura ch'avaarnọng pa Midiyan, am-afọra, akwu attara k'ẹdọhbh cha mgbakkọhbh sa bẹ am-akhe akamẹl pabẹ k'ẹdọhngi.
\v 27 Wa Gideọn otzima gol osi ẹphọd, kw'ọtzọk ohok k'Ọphra kw'ode obhon kwẹ. Wa anọng p'Israẹl biphyir an-asi azaaza-kpen atzima akpobha ẹphọd nda, odik nwa on-ode ọyak ọnang Gideọn ttara ẹhọhmmọr chẹ.
\s1 Obo kwa Gideọn
\p 
\v 28 Mẹ wọ, wa anọng pa Midiyan awobha k'irekhirek kw'anọng p'Israẹl, bẹ ẹfa manda dani dọk kafhasi. Anọng p'Israẹl an-aruk k'odidiri ka cho arọbh afa, k'ogbe kwa Gideọn orukhi akpen biphyir.
\p 
\v 29 Iwa Jerub-Baal kw'ode nnwa kwa Joash ọkpa nnam ọtza oruk k'obhon kwẹ.
\v 30 Wa kẹ ọkhaam panọng k'ọhaabh, ọkhaama va p'ijinọng arọbh attaan obhiri jobh.
\v 31 Ọkkọra-kwanọng kwẹ kw'orukhi ka Shẹkẹm obiro ọmmaan-ẹ nnwa kw'ijinọng, kw'okpen Abimẹlẹk.
\v 32 Wa Gideọn kw'ode nnwa kwa Joash ope da ọkk'ọtzama, bẹ anọhng-ẹ k'epekhubh ch'otte Joash k'Ọphra k'obhon kw'Abiez.
\p 
\v 33 Mada Gideọn ọkk'ọpa, anọng p'Israẹl abira asi azaaza-kpen atza akpobha ikha sa Baal. Bẹ asi ọkha f'okpen Baal-Bẹrit akpobha,
\v 34 anọng p'Israẹl akpa nnam abọra Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kwabẹ kw'okk'bẹ ọkkaana ọrọbha ka mbọhk s'attattaanganọng pabẹ biphyir p'akhọri bẹ.
\v 35 Mẹ wọ e, wa bẹ ọphyaam kabira asi anang ẹkhọmmọr cha Jerub-Baal (kw'okpen Gideọn) k'idik-jibhada s'ọkk'ọsa ọnang anọng p'Israẹl.
\c 9
\s1 Achibhi-tzama p'Abimẹlẹk
\p 
\v 1 Iwa Abimẹlẹk kw'ode nnwa kwa Jerub-Baal ofon ọtza okhebha vọkka p'ọkka ka Shẹkẹm, ọmaana ochi f'ọkka biphyir, oben bẹ bi,
\v 2 “Bọbh ammaana pa Shẹkẹm biphyir bi, ‘Yan wọ ojibh bọng abẹ: bi va arọbh attaan obhiri jobh biphyir pa Jerub-Baal adabh bọng, ọmaana bi, oyok wani kẹ-kẹ ọdabh bọng?’ Bọng jima bi, kaam wọ nde izi sabọng.”
\p 
\v 3 Mada vọkka atzọk idik nna biphyir agbaak anọng pa Shẹkẹm, anọng mba akhera bi, bẹ atzọn Abimẹlẹk abẹ, aben bi, “Kẹ wọ ode ọgbaanọkka kwaman e.”
\v 4 Bẹ atzọkha ashẹkẹl pa silva arọbh attaan obhiri jobh k'ọhọhm kwa Baal-Bẹrit anang-ẹ, Abimẹlẹk otzima bẹ ọtzọkha akparaari-nọng bani bi, bẹ ade akhaan-nọng pẹ.
\v 5 Ofona ochina k'ọhọhm kw'otte k'Ọphra, ọtza obe k'itzakpa rani ofhu votte pẹ anọng arọbh attaan obhiri jobh, p'ade va pa Jerub-Baal. Yina, wa Jotam kw'ode okponga-nnam-nwa kwa Jerub-Baal, ọrọbh ọtza ochubha.
\v 6 Mando kw'anọng pa Shẹkẹm biphyir, ọmaana anọng pa Bet-Milo atza atzobha abaanga echi ch'ideden cha oak, k'ọtza kwa bẹ afhu ebebe ka Shẹkẹm, ifha bẹ asi Abimẹlẹk ọvaarnọng.
\p 
\v 7 Mada bẹ agbaakhi Jotam odik nwa, ovura k'egbegbeho cha Gerizim ebir-ebir, ogwon bẹ, oben bi, “Bọng yong-m itzọhng, bọbọng anọng pa Shẹkẹm, ifha Ibinọkpaabyi oyonga bọng itzọhng.
\v 8 Wa ewu dani, nchi mfon bi, nda ndekha ọvaarnọng kwabẹ. Sẹ mfona nda mben echi ch'oliv bi, ‘De ọvaarnọng kwaman.’
\p 
\v 9 “Yina, echi ch'oliv ebhina bi, ‘Ma, kaam nkwọhbha ana paam oyiyin pa bẹ am-atzima anang ikha, ọmaana anọngẹya ikpokpobha, ifha nda ndabh ẹvaar cha nchi o?’
\p 
\v 10 “Ayongi mẹ, nchi nna nda mben echi cha fig bi, ‘Kwu de man ọvaarnọng.’
\p 
\v 11 “Yina, echi cha fig ebhina bi, ‘Ma kaam ntte achiduk paam p'ajibh-ojibh abira adaam-ọdaam ọbọhk, nkwu ndabh ẹvaar cha nchi o?’
\p 
\v 12 “Mando kwa nchi nna mbeni echi cha grep bi, ‘Kwu de ọvaarnọng kwaman.’
\p 
\v 13 “Yina, echi cha grep ebhina bi, ‘Ma, kaam nkwọbha atzuk daaman-daam paam, p'am-anang ikha ọmaana anọngeya ọdadaami oyiyin, nkwu ndabh ẹvaar cha nchi o?’
\p 
\v 14 “K'ekponga-nnam, nchi nna biphyir nda mben ọkkaangi bi, ‘Kwu de man ọvaarnọng.’
\p 
\v 15 “Ọkkaangi oben nchi bi, ‘Idikha k'odik-ọkka bọng arori bi, abyeng-m ana k'eho asi-m ọvaarnọng kwabọng, bọng kwu kwokha ọwọhng k'odiriji kwaam. Yina, oni mando ode, tte ekpon eyin k'ọkkaangi ẹkwọmi ọbhọmi-mancheni kwa Lebanọn!’
\p 
\v 16 “Bọng akk'abarada atzọkha, abira asi odik kw'ojibh-ojibh bi, bọng asi Abimẹlẹk ọvaarnọng o? Bọng akk'ejibha asa anang Jerub-Baal ọmaana ẹhọhmmọr chẹ ẹ? Bọng akk'asa anang-ẹ mach'ọban bi, ira bọng aso o?
\v 17 Bọng jima bi, iwa otte kwaam orim erima kabọng ka nho, okhe akpen pẹ ka dama-dama, ifha ọrọbha bọng k'ihem s'anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Midiyan.
\v 18 Yina, k'ewu cha mayina, bọng akk'abhakhi arima ẹhọhmmọr ch'otte kwaam abẹ. Bọng akk'va pẹ p'ijinọng anọng arọbh attaan obhiri jobh afha k'itzakpa rani. Bọng asi Abimẹlẹk kw'ode nnwa kw'obira kwanọng kwẹ ọvaarnọng kw'anọng pa Shẹkẹm, okhuri da ode ọgbaanọkka kwabọng.
\v 19 Mẹ wọ, bọng akk'abarada ọtzọkha, abira asi odik kw'ojibh-ojibh bi, bọng asi Abimẹlẹk ọvaarnọng o? Bọng akk'ejibha asa anang Jerub-Baal ọmaana ẹhọhmmọr chẹ mayina, tte Abimẹlẹk ode ottem-daamiji kwabọng, bọbọng abira ade ottem-daamiji kwẹ!
\v 20 Yina, bọng ani mando atzima asi, tte ekpon ch'efon k'Abimẹlẹk echi bọng anọng pa Shẹkẹm, ọmaana anọng pa Bet-Milo. Tte ekpon efona ka bọbọng anọng pa Shẹkẹm ọmaana Bet-Milo, echi Abimẹlẹk!”
\p 
\v 21 Mando kwa Jotam ọrọbhi ochina k'obhon kwa Beer, ọtza oruk kẹ okhuri ojora f'ọgbaanotte, Abimẹlẹk.
\p 
\v 22 Mada Abimẹlẹk okk'Israẹl ọdabha ka cho attaan,
\v 23 Ibinọkpaabyi otte egwugwuma-tzama ọbọhk ẹnwa Abimẹlẹk ọmaana ammaana pa Shẹkẹm, kw'osi bẹ an-agaangi eho anang Abimẹlẹk.
\v 24 Wa Ibinọkpaabyi osi kwẹ mando, ifha otzima otzukha odik kwa Abimẹlẹk ọmaana ammaana pa Shẹkẹm asi, p'atzor-ẹ afhu va p'ijinọng arọbh attaan obhiri jobh pa Jerub-Baal, abira abyengi izi sabẹ.
\v 25 Wa anọng pa Shẹkẹm an-abhakh-ẹ abẹ, bẹ atzọhm ajinọng p'afon atza achubha k'akkadeden pa mgbegbeho am-abọkha anọng p'areng mẹ ekpo ana. Wa bẹ atzọkha odik nwa agbaak Abimẹlẹk.
\p 
\v 26 M'ogbe nwa wa Gaal kw'ode nnwa kw'Ebed otzima ẹnọmma chẹ obina ochina ka Shẹkẹm. Wa ammaana p'ẹnọmma nda akhaam ekhera ka Gaal.
\v 27 Mada bẹ akk'afona ayin k'iwoni atza apha grep atzima asi atzuk, bẹ an-asi ọdadaami k'ọkhapa kw'ọkha fabẹ. Bẹ am-achi abira agwo, am-asaakhi Abimẹlẹk.
\v 28 Mẹ wọ ofon Gaal kw'ode nnwa kw'Ebed oben bi, “Anyi wọ ode Abimẹlẹk, kw'ira maman anọng pa Shẹkẹm on-owobha irekhirek kwẹ o? Kẹ arang ode nnwa kwa Jerub-Baal, kwa Zebul ojem mbọhk ka nnam o? On-orenga yan mowobha k'irekhirek kw'Abimẹlẹk? Bọng mọhakha eho ọnang itta Hamọr, kw'ode otte kwa Shẹkẹm.
\v 29 Ira anọng mba awobh k'irekhirek kwaam! Ira kaam ndim-ẹ. Ira mben Abimẹlẹk bi, ‘Tzima arim-egbong pọ biphyir ayin ka!’ ”
\p 
\v 30 Mada Zebul kw'ode ọdabh-ẹkhọma ch'odedenmon, ọbhaang odik kwa Gaal kw'ode nnwa kw'Ebed ọgbaakhi, ettem epyibh-ẹ itzama-itzama.
\v 31 Orenga ka ndubhama ọtzọhm akkaabh-nkkaabha ochena Abimẹlẹk, oben bi, “Gaal kw'ode nnwa kw'Ebed ọmaana vọkka pẹ akk'akwa ka Shẹkẹm, akwu achọhma ẹkhọhr k'odedenmon atzima atzor-ọ.
\v 32 Mẹ wọ, kọ bina m'erungi ttara ajinọng pọ, bọng akwu ayima atzik bẹ k'iwoni.
\v 33 K'ekpebha mada ewuchen eyin, bọng bina atza arima odedenmon nwa abẹ. K'ogbe kwa Gaal ọmaana ajinọng pẹ ayin ka bi, bẹ akwu arima bọng abẹ, bọng dima ọphaangi nwuma arima bẹ abẹ.”
\p 
\v 34 Mando kw'Abimẹlẹk, ọmaana arim-egbong pẹ biphyir abin orenga m'erungi, bẹ abhaangi for sabẹ ka ngaan nna afona atza achubha k'obe-k'obe abaanga Shẹkẹm.
\v 35 Mando kwa Gaal kw'ode nnwa kw'Ebed okk'ofona ọtza obe k'ẹbaakhamma ch'odedenmon otzik, otzor m'ogbe kw'Abimẹlẹk ọmaana arim-egbong pẹ afon k'ibe sa bẹ achubh, ayin ka.
\p 
\v 36 Mada Gaal ore bẹ, oben Zebul bi, “Kkeri anọng kana, p'am-afona ka mgbegbeho ahakha e!”
\p Zebul obhina bi, “Kọ are agbagba pa mgbegbeho, an-achibhi bi, anọngẹya bọ p'are.”
\p 
\v 37 Yina, Gaal obiro oben bi, “Kkere anọng kana am-afona k'egbegbeho ebira ahakha e, ẹkhaan dani ebire ekwuma kana ọkkadeden kw'echi ch'abọhnganọng e.”
\p 
\v 38 Mẹ wọ ofon, Zebul oben-ẹ bi, “Ẹmma ma dọk kaben o, kọ arang ewu nda abeni bi, ‘Anyi wọ ode Abimẹlẹk kwa maman on-owobha irekhirek kwẹ ẹ?’ Ajinọng mba arang p'ewu nda am-alukh o? Yin k'iyaan atza arima bẹ abẹ!”
\p 
\v 39 Mando kwa Gaal otzim ammaana pa Shẹkẹm eden, ọtza orima Abimẹlẹk abẹ.
\v 40 Abimẹlẹk okhubh-ẹ maa, opyiri k'ẹbaakhamma ch'odedenmon, bẹ afhu anọng haabhada mada bẹ am-arọbh.
\v 41 Wa Abimẹlẹk ọtza owobha k'obhon kw'Aruma. Zebul e, okhubh Gaal ọmaana ẹnọmma chẹ ka Shẹkẹm.
\p 
\v 42 Ewu ehobh mẹ, anọng pa Shẹkẹm afona ayin k'iwoni sabẹ, bẹ atzọkha odik nwa agbaak Abimẹlẹk.
\v 43 Mando kw'ọtzọk ajinọng pẹ ọbhaangi ka ngaan nttaan bẹ afona atza achubha k'iwoni, atzik. Mada ore da anọng mba am-afona k'odedenmon ayin ka, obina ọtza orima bẹ abẹ.
\v 44 Mando kw'Abimẹlẹk ọmaana ngaan nna sa nwobh ttar-ẹ, arọbhi achina itzitzikha-itzitzikha atza abe k'ẹbaakhamma ch'adimi k'odedenmon. Ngaan mfa ngwubh ayok p'awobh k'iwoni, afhu bẹ.
\v 45 M'ewu nduma biphyir Abimẹlẹk ochina ororo orima odedenmon abẹ maa, ọbọkh-ẹ, obiro ofhu anọng p'obhon nwa. Mando kwa okhibhi odedenmon nwa yina ọn-ọtzọk onung ọnyaani m'akhọra obhon nwa.
\p 
\v 46 Mada ammaana p'akkeribe sa Shẹkẹm abhaang odik nwa, bẹ arọbh achina k'ichubhabe s'ọhọhm kw'Ẹl-Bẹrit.
\v 47 K'ogbe kw'Abimẹlẹk ọbhaang bi, bẹ akk'atzobha kẹ,
\v 48 kẹ ọmaana ajinọng pẹ biphyir avura achina k'egbegbeho cha Zalmọn. Abimẹlẹk ọtzọkha ẹbar ọkpaara abọhnga bani p'echi, p'otzini ọnana k'ẹbabaang. Ọnang ajinọng p'awobh ttar-ẹ ẹfa bi, “Ẹbhar-ẹbhar! Bọng si macha bọng are-m da nsi ma!”
\v 49 Mando kw'ajinọng mba biphyir abira akpaara achi-bọhnga, atzima atzọn Abimẹlẹk abẹ. Bẹ atzọkha sẹ atzobha k'ichubhabe, bẹ atzọkha ekpon akhe akpori anọng p'awobh k'ichubhabe nna ẹtzaanga. Mẹ wọ ofon, anọng biphyir p'awobh k'ibe s'akkeribe sa Shẹkẹm, ajinọng ọmaana panọng p'apyiri nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh jobh, abira ape.
\p 
\v 50 Abimẹlẹk obina mẹ ọtza ọkhọri obhon kwa Tẹbẹz okhe k'ottem ọbọkh-ẹ.
\v 51 Wa k'odedenmon ẹtzaanga, ọkhaam ibe s'akkeribe sa bẹ abaabh-ọbhaabh s'ajinọng ọmaana panọng akwu attara k'anọng p'odedenmon biphyir akk'arọbha atza achubha. Bẹ agbak akpori for sabẹ k'ẹtzaanga, avura atza abe k'ẹyọhng ch'ibe nna.
\v 52 Abimẹlẹk ofona ochina k'ibe s'akkeribe bi, ọtza orima anọng mba abẹ. Yina, mada opyiri k'ẹbaakhamma ch'ibe nna bi okhe sẹ ekpon,
\v 53 mando kwa kwanọng wani otte ẹtzakpa dani ọbọhk k'ẹrọng, ettem-ẹ m'eho ẹbhaakha Abimẹlẹk eho.
\p 
\v 54 Oyeri otzim-egbongkpo kwẹ m'ẹbhar-ẹbhar, oben-ẹ bi, “Tzọr ọkkangkkaang kwọ afhu-m, ifha bẹ aningi abeni bi, ‘Kwanọng wọ ọfhu-m’ ” Mando kw'ọtzọhmnọng kwẹ ọtzọri ọkkangkkaang okhum-ẹ, ope.
\v 55 Mada anọng p'Israẹl are bi, Abimẹlẹk ọkk'ọpa, bẹ akpa nnam abhana.
\p 
\v 56 Mando wọ kw'Ibinọkpaabyi oreng otzukha itzama s'Abimẹlẹk ọkk'ọsa ọnang otte kwẹ, da ofhu votte pẹ anọng arọbh attaan obhiri jobh.
\v 57 Wa Ibinọkpaabyi obiro osi ajinọng pa Shẹkẹm ape k'itzama sa bẹ asi biphyir. Wa ẹmma cha Jotam kw'ode nnwa kwa Jerub-Baal ẹbọkha bẹ.
\c 10
\s1 Tola kw'ode osi-aponga kw'Israẹl
\p 
\v 1 K'ogbe kw'Abimẹlẹk ọkk'ọpa, ojinọng kw'okpen Tola kw'ofon k'ẹkhọma ch'Isaaka, obiro ode nnwa kwa Pua kw'ode nnwa kwa Dodo, obina bi, ọkkaana anọng p'Israẹl. Wa orukhi ka Shamir, k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim.
\v 2 Wa kẹ ode osi-aponga k'Israẹl ka cho ẹrọbh obhiri attaan, yina on-ope, bẹ anọhng-ẹ ka Shamir.
\s1 Jair kw'ode osi-aponga kw'Israẹl
\p 
\v 3 Iwa ọnọng kw'ojem mẹ, ode Jair kw'ofon Gilead, kw'iwa ode osi-aponga k'Israẹl ka cho ẹrọbh obhiri afa.
\v 4 Wa kẹ obhoni ajinọng ẹrọbh obhiri jobh, p'ayaari nnyanyaang ẹrọbh obhiri jobh. Wa bẹ abira abaabha ibhon ẹrọbh obhiri jobh ka Gilead sa maa, apyiri ma bẹ ayeri sẹ Havot-Jair.
\v 5 Mada Jair ope, bẹ anọhng-ẹ ka Kamọn.
\s1 Jephta kw'ode osi-aponga kw'Israẹl
\p 
\v 6 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl abira asi ebibya k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi. Bẹ akpobha ikha sa Baal ọmaana s'Ashtọrẹt, ọmaana s'Aram, ọmaana sa Sidọn, ọmaana sa Moab, ọmaana s'Ammọn ttara ikha s'anọng pa Philistiya. Wa anọng p'Israẹl akpa nnam abọra Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, bẹ kẹ dọk kakpobh.
\v 7 Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọdọkhi ettem otzima otzor anọng p'Israẹl. Ọtzọkha bẹ okhe anọng pa Philistiya, ọmaana anọng p'Ammọn ka mbọhk,
\v 8 p'apfuri bẹ abira afhu bẹ. Wa okhe anọng p'Israẹl biphyir k'ihem, k'okhubha kw'ewuchen em-eyin kwa Jọrdan ka Gilead, kw'ode ẹkhọma ch'anọng p'Amọr, ka cho chi obhiri attaan.
\v 9 Wa anọng p'ẹkhọma ch'Ammọn abira ajekha ọraanga kwa Jọrdan, atza arima erima ọmaana ẹkhọma cha Juda, ọmaana cha Bẹnjamin ọmaana ch'Ephraim; wa Israẹl owobh k'ọmmamma kw'ideden.
\v 10 Mẹ wọ ofon, anọng p'Israẹl abhom ẹmọng anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, aben bi, “Maman okk'ẹkhọhngkwuri ọsa k'itzitzikha sọ, mokk'nnam ọkpa ọbọra Ibinọkpaabyi kwaman, mokpobha ikha sa Baal.”
\p 
\v 11 Iwa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi obhina anọng p'Israẹl bi, “K'ogbe kw'iwa anọng p'Ijip, ọmaana p'Amọr, ọmaana p'Ammọn, ọmaana pa Philistiya,
\v 12 ọmaana pa Sidọn, ọmaana p'Amalẹk, ttara anọng pa Maọn akhe bọng k'ihem, bọng abhom ayer-m bi, nkkaana bọng, wa bọng kinkkaan nnọbha bọng ka mbọhk sabẹ o?
\v 13 Yina, bọng akk'nnam akpa abọr-m, bọng akpobha ekpo ẹdọdọk. Mẹ wọ osi, kaam bọng dọk kínkkaana.
\v 14 Bọng nọhng atza abhom anang ikha sa bọng akk'atzekha bi, akpobha. Tte sẹ ikkaana bọng k'ogbe kwa dama-dama!”
\p 
\v 15 Yina, anọng p'Israẹl aben Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi bi, “Maman ọkk'ẹkhọngkwuri ọsa. Kọ tzima man asi odik kpenamkpen kw'ọdaakh-ọ, yina, tzotzokhaan kkaana man e.”
\v 16 Mando kwa bẹ avọhkhi ikha s'iwobh kabẹ k'ottem, bẹ an-akpobha Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi. Mẹ wọ ofon, Ibinọkpaabyi ọkkaana anọng p'Israẹl k'ihem sabẹ.
\p 
\v 17 K'ogbe kw'anọng p'Ammọn adabhi egbong abhing ka Gilead, anọng p'Israẹl atzobha ibe rani, abhing ka Mizpa.
\v 18 Adeho p'anọng pa Gilead abhakhi aben ayok bi, “Ọnọng manda wani kw'óde ocheden-nọng kw'orima anọng p'Ammọn abẹ, kẹ wọ óde oho kw'anọng p'arukhi ka Gilẹad biphyir.”
\c 11
\p 
\v 1 Iwa Jẹphta kw'ofon Gilead ode okkengitza kw'ideden. Wa otte okpen Gilead; ọkka kwẹ ode ọzaaza-kwanọng.
\v 2 Wa kwanọng kwa Gilẹad obiro ọmaan-ẹ va p'ijinọng. Mada va mba abari, bẹ akhubh Jẹphta, aben bi, “Kọ ekkema manda dani ka man k'ẹhọhmmọr kakhaam, okhuri bi, kọ ade nnwa kwa kwanọng ọdọdọk.”
\v 3 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa Jẹphta obina oji votte pẹ, ọtza oruk k'irerek sa Tob, kẹ kwa ẹkhaan ch'akparari-nọng bani atzọn-ẹ abẹ, abira awobha ttar-ẹ.
\p 
\v 4 K'ogbe mẹ, wa anọng p'Ammọn am-arima anọng p'Israẹl abẹ.
\v 5 M'ogbe nwuma kw'anọng p'Ammọn am-arima anọng p'Israẹl abẹ, adeho pa Gilead afona bi, atza atzọkha Jẹphta k'irerek sa Tob.
\v 6 Wa bẹ aben Jẹphta bi, “Kwu de man oho kw'arim-egbong, ifha mọfha orima anọng p'Ammọn abẹ.”
\p 
\v 7 Iwa Jẹphta oben adeho pa Gilead bi, “Wa bọng kaam kattaang maa, bọng akhubh-m k'ẹhọhmmọr ch'otte kwaam o? Okhuri yan kwa bọng an-abira arọbh akwu ka kaam k'ogbe kwa dama-dama?”
\p 
\v 8 Adeho pa Gilead aben Jẹphta bi, “Kaambi obiro ode mando, mayina mọn-ọtzọn kọ abẹ; kwu tzọn man abẹ, mọtza orima anọng p'Ammọn abẹ, kkeri kọ wọ áde oho kwaman biphyir p'orukhi ka Gilead.”
\p 
\v 9 Jẹphta obhina anọng pa Gilead bi, “Idikha bọng atzim-m mkpa nnam nda nnima anọng p'Ammọn abẹ, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi osi ngema bẹ, na kaam nde bọng oho k'odik-ọkka a?”
\p 
\v 10 Iwa adedennọng pa Gilead abhina Jẹphta bi, “Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi wọ ode nttẹsẹ kwaman, mósi-osi mach'abeni.”
\v 11 Mẹ wọ ofon, Jẹphta ọtzọn adedennọng pa Gilead abẹ, bẹ asẹ-ẹ oho kwabẹ ọmaana odeho kw'arim-egbong. Mando kwa Jẹphta obiro ọgbaak atzim p'ira ọgbaakhi k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ka Mizpa.
\p 
\v 12 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa Jẹphta ọtzọhm akkaabh-nkkaabha p'atza abọbh ọvaarnọng kw'anọng p'Ammọn bi, “Ottotto kwaam ode yan, kw'arim ẹkhọma chaam abẹ o?”
\p 
\v 13 Iwa ọvaarnọng kw'anọng p'Ammọn obhina akkaabh-nkkaabha pa Jẹphta bi, “Mada iwa anọng p'Israẹl abin k'Ijip akwu, bẹ atzọk irerek saam ttẹwọr k'ọraanga kw'Arnọn maa, apyiri k'ọraanga kwa Jabọk, atzima atza apyiri k'ọraanga kwa Jọrdan. Kọ na tte sẹ ọbọhk anang-m \it bi bẹm\it*.”
\p 
\v 14 Iwa Jẹphta ọtzọhm akkaabh-nkkaabha akpa nnam k'ọvaarnọng kw'anọng p'Ammọn,
\v 15 oben bi:
\pm “Ma wọ ode odik kwa kaam Jẹphta mgbaakhi bi: anọng p'Israẹl bẹ irerek sa Moab obiro ode irerek s'anọng p'Ammọn, katzọk.
\v 16 Yina, k'ogbe kw'iwa bẹ abin k'Ijip, wa anọng p'Israẹl areng k'ebherede apyiri k'Ẹraanga-khora, akwọbha achina ka Kadẹsh.
\v 17 Wa anọng p'Israẹl atzọhm akkaabh-nkkaabha k'ọvaarnọng kw'Edom, aben bi, ‘Tte morenga k'ẹkhọma chọ ọkwobha,’ yina, ọvaarnọng kw'Edom bẹ itzọhng koyong. Wa bẹ abira atzọhm ẹkkaabha nda anang ọvaarnọng kwa Moab, kẹ obiro obhum. Mẹ wọ ofon, wa anọng p'Israẹl an-awobha ka Kadẹsh.
\p 
\v 18 “Ayongi mẹ, wa anọng p'Israẹl arenga k'ibe s'anọng an-arukhi, k'ọkhaan-ọkhaan kw'Edom ọmaana kwa Moab. Bẹ arenga k'okhubha kw'ewuchen em-eyin ka Moab, atza abhing k'okhubha kw'ọraanga kw'Arnọn. Wa bẹ k'ẹkhọma cha Moab kadimi da iwa Arnọn ode enem chabẹ.
\p 
\v 19 “Mẹ wọ ofon, wa anọng p'Israẹl atzọhm akkaabh-nkkaabha ka Sihon kw'ode ọvaarnọng kw'anọng p'Amọr, kw'ọdabhi ẹvaar ka Hẹshbọn, aben-ẹ bi, ‘Tte morenga k'ẹkhọma chọ, ochina ka man k'ibe.’
\v 20 Wa Sihon anọng p'Israẹl k'odik-ọkka kọtzọk, kẹ wọ osi bẹ ọbọhk kotte bẹ arenga k'ẹkhọma chẹ. Wa ọtzọhm arim-egbong pẹ atza abhing ka Jahaz, arima anọng p'Israẹl abẹ.
\p 
\v 21 “Mẹ wọ ofon, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kw'Israẹl, ọtzọkha Sihon ọmaana arim-egbong pẹ biphyir okhe anọng p'Israẹl ka mbọhk, bẹ akhema bẹ. Wa anọng p'Israẹl atzọkha irerek biphyir s'anọng p'Amọr p'iwa arukhi mẹ ẹkhọma nduma.
\v 22 Bẹ attẹwọr k'Arnọn atzọkha irerek s'anọng p'Amọr biphyir maa, apyiri ka Jabọk ọmaana k'ebherede maa, apyiri ka Jọrdan.
\p 
\v 23 “Mada Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kw'Israẹl okk'anọng p'Amọr okhubha k'itzitzikha s'anọng pẹ p'Israẹl, bọng ẹfa cha kọ akhaam bi, abira akpa nnam atzọkha irerek nna a?
\v 24 Idikha Kẹmọsh kw'ode ọkha fabọng, ọnangi bọng ọttọhk bọng katzọkha a? Mando kw'ode ttara man bi, ọttọhk kpenamkpen f'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kwaman ọnangi man, mọtzọkh-ọtzọkha.
\v 25 Yan kwa kọ ajibhi ayọnga Balak kw'ode nnwa kwa Zipọr, kw'ode ọvaarnọng kwa Moab? Mada ogbe odede, ọkk'ẹkhọhr ọsa ọmaana anọng p'Israẹl, yina ira on-orim bẹ abẹ o?
\v 26 Ka cho arọbh chi kw'anọng p'Israẹl arukhi ka Hẹshbọn ọmaana k'Aroa ọmaana k'ibhon s'iwobh ikhọri bẹ, ttara k'abhobhona biphyir p'awobh k'ọkkadeden da achin k'Arnọn. Okhuri yan kw'iwa bọng ani sẹ k'ogbe nwuma atzọk?
\v 27 Kaam kọ itzama kinsi. Yina, kọ am-achibhi itzama bi, arim-m abẹ. Tte Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ọsi-aponga, ọttọhna aponga mba ọnang anọng p'Israẹl ọmaana anọng p'Ammọn.”
\m 
\v 28 Kaambi mẹ wọ, ọvaarnọng kw'Ammọn ẹkkaabha nda cha Jẹphta ọtzọhmi ọnang-ẹ, itzọhng koyong.
\p 
\v 29 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa egwugwuma ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ch'ẹfa ẹnwa Jẹphta. Ojekha ka Gilead ọmaana ka Manasẹ, orenga ka Mizpa kwa Gilead, ọtza orima anọng p'Ammọn abẹ.
\v 30 Wa Jẹphta osi echekhi ọnang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, oben bi, “Idikha atte anọng p'Ammọn ọbọhk anang-m,
\v 31 mada mmana da ngema anọng p'Ammọn, ọttọhk kpenamkpen f'ochi eden ofona k'ọhọhm kwaam okwu ọgọm-m, fẹ óde f'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, ḿbiri ndima fẹ ńsi ẹjafọhni ẹkwọmichẹ.”
\p 
\v 32 Mando kwa Jẹphta ofon ọtza orima anọng p'Ammọn abẹ. Wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi otte anọng mba ọbọhk ọnang-ẹ.
\v 33 Wa Jẹphta okhema ibhon ẹrọbh k'Aroer ọmaana, k'okhubha kwa Minit maa, apyiri k'Abẹl-Keramin. Mẹ wọ ofon, wa anọng p'Ammọn an-awobha irekhirek kw'anọng p'Israẹl.
\p 
\v 34 Mada Jẹphta opyiri k'ọhọhm kwẹ ka Mizpa, wa ọnọng kw'oyini k'iyaan ọgọm-ẹ kode, oyongi ominanwa kwẹ kw'ode nnwa obungikwẹ kw'ọkhaam, kw'otzubhi ebin otzor k'okhira kw'achangchangkpa. Akhiri ominanwa nwa aji, wa nnwa ọdọdọk ode kw'ijinọng obiro ode kw'ikwanọng kọkhaam.
\v 35 Mada otte ọrẹ-ẹ, ọbọkha ọbara f'ọfọr ọjaakhi obhom, oben bi, “Kpe e, nnwa kwaam! Akk'asa chua ọbọkh-m, ẹfa ẹkk'aam ẹha. Kaam nkk'echekhi nsa k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi cha nni nnam mfha mkpa mbọra.”
\p 
\v 36 Nnwa obhina bi, “Otte kwaam, kọ akk'echekhi asa anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi e. Tzim-m si mach'akk'achekhi, da Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọkk'anọng p'Ammọn, p'ade attattaanga-nọng pọ, okhema ọnang-ọ.
\v 37 Yina, tte mphyem-ọ odik nwa wani, nang-m aphe afa, ifha kaam ọmaana ayokh-omina paam mobhom ọkpaanga k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho, okhuri da kaam nni odim ḿba maa, ikhina ogbe ode.”
\p 
\v 38 Otte obhina bi, “Kọ rọhng.” Ọttẹ-ẹ ọbọhk ofona k'aphe afa. Kẹ ọmaana ayokh-omina pẹ afona achina k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho atza abhom amọng kẹ, okhuri da ominanwa nwa oni odim ọ́ba maa, ogbe ode.
\v 39 Mada aphe afa akk'akwọbha, okhuna okwu okhebha otte, otte otzim-ẹ osi mach'okk'ochekhi. Wa ominanwa nwa ojinọng otzim oronga.
\p Ma wọ kw'ẹmmaana ch'anọng p'Israẹl efon,
\v 40 cha ka cho kpenamkpen aminava p'Israẹl, am-afona k'iwu inna atzima ajima ominanwa kwa Jẹphta, kw'ofon Gilead.
\c 12
\s1 Ẹkhọhr cha Jẹphta ọmaana anọng p'Ephraim asi
\p 
\v 1 Iwa anọng p'Ephraim ayeri arim-egbong pabẹ atzobha, bẹ ajekha k'okhubha kwa Zaphon. Bẹ aben Jẹphta bi, “Okhuri yan kw'atza arima anọng p'Ammọn abẹ, man kayeri mọtzọn-ọ abẹ? Mada akk'mando asa, mọ́kwọm-ọ k'ekpon ttara ọhọhm kwọ.”
\p 
\v 2 Jẹphta obhina bi, “Erima cha kaam ọmaana anọng paam morim ttara anọng p'Ammọn, ede erima ch'ẹgaangi-ọgaangi. Chibhi da nyeri bọng, bọng kaam ka mbọhk sabẹ kakaan.
\v 3 Mada nne bi, bọng kaam kakkaana, kaam nna nkhera obo njekha nda nnima anọng p'Ammọn abẹ. Wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi osi-m ngema bẹ. Ode yan kwa bọng an-akwu bi, akwu arim-m abẹ o?”
\p 
\v 4 Iwa Jẹphta on-oyeri anọng pa Gilead otzobha, otzima bẹ ọtza orima anọng p'Ephraim abẹ. Wa anọng pa Gilead afhu anọng p'Ephraim, okhuri da iwa anọng p'Ephraim akk'abena bi, “Bọbọng anọng pa Gilead ade arọbhi-mgbong p'afon Ephraim ọmaana Manasẹ.”
\v 5 Wa anọng pa Gilead akpa obe f'ogbin-ogbin k'ọraanga kwa Jọrdan f'ochin k'Ephraim. Ogbe kpenamkpen kw'ọnọng kw'Ephraim kw'ọrọbhi ọnaanga, obeni bi, “Tte njekha k'okhubha,” ajinọng pa Gilead abọbh-ẹ bi, “Kọ afon Ephraim o?” Idikha obhin bi, “Mma,”
\v 6 bẹ aben-ẹ bi, “Ode mando ben bi, ‘Shibolẹt.’ ” Idikha obeni bi, “Sibolẹt, ” okhuri da ọnọng nwuma oni ọwọhng nwa ejibha ọfha oyeri, bẹ abọkh-ẹ afhu k'obe f'ogbin-ogbin k'ọraanga kwa Jọrdan. M'ogbe nwa, wa bẹ afhu anọng p'Ephraim nnọhna arọbh afa obhiri chi.
\p 
\v 7 Iwa Jẹphta ode osi-aponga k'Israẹl ka cho azadani. Wa Jẹphta kw'ofon Gilead ope, bẹ anọhng-ẹ k'obhon wani ka Gilead.
\s1 Ibzan ọmaana Ẹlọn ttara Abdọn akwu ade asi-aponga k'Israẹl
\p 
\v 8 Mada Jẹphta ọkk'ọpa, Ibzan kw'ofon Bẹtẹlẹhẹm, okwu ode osi-aponga k'Israẹl.
\v 9 Wa kẹ ọkhaam adikkobh ẹrọbh obhiri jobh, ọmaana aminava ẹrọbh obhiri jobh. Wa ọtzọkha aminava pẹ ọnang ajinọng pa nnọmma ndọdọk k'ọbada, obiro ọtza ọtzọkha aminava ẹrọbh obhiri jobh ka nnọmma ndọdọk, ochena adikkobh pẹ bi, bẹ aba. Wa Ibzan ode osi-aponga k'Israẹl ka cho azenamfa.
\v 10 Wa Ibzan ope, bẹ anọhng-ẹ ka Bẹtẹlẹhẹm.
\p 
\v 11 Mada Ibzan ọkk'ọpa, Ẹlọn kw'ofon Zẹbulun okwu ode osi-aponga k'Israẹl ka cho jobh.
\v 12 Wa Ẹlọn ope, bẹ anọhng-ẹ k'Ayijalọn, k'ẹkhọma cha Zebulun.
\p 
\v 13 Mada Ẹlọn ọkk'ọpa, Abdọn kw'ode nnwa kwa Hilẹl, kw'ofon Piraton, okwu ode osi-aponga k'Israẹl.
\v 14 Wa kẹ ọkhaam adikkobh arọbh afa ọmaana va pa va p'ade ajinọng ẹrọbh obhiri jobh, p'ayaari ka nnyanyaang arọbh attaan obhiri jobh. Wa kẹ ode osi-aponga k'Israẹl ka cho azenanttaan.
\v 15 Wa Abdọn kw'ode nnwa kwa Hilẹl ope, bẹ anọhng-ẹ ka Piraton k'ẹkhọma ch'Ephraim k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'anọng p'Amalẹk.
\c 13
\s1 Ẹ̀mmáaná cha Samson
\p 
\v 1 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl abira asi ebibya k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi. Mẹ wọ osi, wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi otte bẹ ọbọhk, bẹ awobha k'irekhirek kw'anọng pa Philistiya, ka cho arọbh afa.
\p 
\v 2 Iwa ojinọng wani kw'okpen Manoa kw'ofon Zora, k'ẹkhọma cha Dan, ọkhaam kwanọng kw'ode ojididima, nnwa kọfha ọmaan.
\v 3 Wa oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oyin kwanọng nwa abẹ, oben bi, “Kọ ade ojididima, nnwa kakhaam, yina, kọ atzima ibhọr otzima amaan nwa kw'ijinọng.
\v 4 Mẹ wọ, kọ atzuk manda bani, kaambi abhinga-tzuk bọ, kàgwo, ọttọhk fa bẹ aphaangi-ọphaangi kàbira achi.
\v 5 Kọ átzima ibhọr otzima amaan nnwa kw'ijinọng kw'ẹkpẹr en-eho chẹ ẹttọhmi, okhuri bi, odikkobh nwa atzuk p'agaangi-ọgaangi kogwo, ẹkpẹr kẹ k'eho kẹ́ttọhmi\f + \fr 13.5 \ft K'eHiburu, ọnọng kw'oni atzuk p'agaangi-ọgaangi ogwo, ẹkpẹr kẹ k'eho kebire ẹttọhmi bẹ ayer-ẹ Nazirit.\f*, óde nnwa kwa bẹ attẹwọr k'ibhọr átte ọbọhk anang Ibinọkpaabyi. Kẹ wọ ótzima anọng eden, ọrọbha anọng p'Israẹl ka mbọhk s'anọng pa Philistiya.”
\p 
\v 6 Mando kwa kwanọng nwa ofon ọtza ọgbaak odim bi, “Ọsẹjaakhi kw'Ibinọkpaabyi oyin-m abẹ. Kẹ okheri oreng-eden kw'Ibinọkpaabyi kw'ojor-ojora. Kaam kẹ ibe s'ofon okwu kimbọbhi, kaam che chẹ kobiro ọgbaak.
\v 7 Yina, kẹ oben-m bi, ‘Kọ átzima ibhọr otzima ámaan nwa kw'ijinọng. Mẹ wọ osi, kọ atzuk manda bani, kaambi abhinga-tzuk bọ, kàgwo. Ọttọhk fa bẹ aphaangi-ọphaangi kàbira achi, okhuri bi, odikkobh nwa atzuk p'agaangi-ọgaangi kógwo, ẹkpẹr kẹ k'eho kẹ́ttọhmi, óde nnwa kwa bẹ attẹwọr k'ibhọr átte ọbọhk anang Ibinọkpaabyi maa, ikhina ope.’ ”
\p 
\v 8 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa Manoa ozi njọhm ọnang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oben bi: “O Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi kọhkha kaam ọtzọhmnọng kwọ inọngkwo. Kaam ngwukh-ọ okhukhi bi, atte ọsẹjaakhi kw'ira atzọhmi achena man ọbọhk, obiro ọkpa nnam ifha okwu okpebhi man odem kwa morenga ọrọk odikkobh nwa kwa bẹ ámaan e.”
\p 
\v 9 Iwa Ibinọkpaabyi ọbhaanga njọhm sa Manoa. Orenga-eden kw'Ibinọkpaabyi obiro oyin kwanọng nwa abẹ, k'ogbe kw'owobh k'owoni; yina, wa odim kwẹ Manoa mẹ kode.
\v 10 Kwanọng nwa ọjaabhi mmo ọtza ọgbaak odim bi, “Ojinọng nwuma kw'ewu nda oyin-m abẹ, okk'obiro akwa e!”
\p 
\v 11 Manoa obina otzor kwanọng kwẹ nnam. Mada okwu okhebha ojinọng nwa, obọbh-ẹ bi, “Kọ wọ ade ojinọng kw'ewu nda agbaakhi kwanọng kwaam odik o?”
\p Obhina bi, “O o, kaam wọ e.”
\p 
\v 12 Mẹ wọ ofon, Manoa ọbọbh-ẹ bi, “K'ogbe kw'atzim pọ ákhaama ẹjaakhi, bọng aphaangi bọ p'odikkobh nwa oruk akpen otzor, obiro osi ọtzọhm otzor o?”
\p 
\v 13 Iwa oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi obhina bi, “Kwanọng kwọ ọkhaambi osi odik kpenamkpen kwa nkk'ẹ mgbaakha bi, osi.
\v 14 Kẹ kọkhaambi ochi ọttọhk manda vani f'ofon ka grep, kọkhaambi ogwo atzuk manda bani, kaambi abhinga-tzuk bọ, kẹ kọkhaambi ochi ọphaangi-ttọhk manda vani. Kẹ ọkhaambi osi odik kpenamkpen kwa nkk'ẹ ndọhna.”
\p 
\v 15 Mẹ wọ ofon, Manoa oben oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi bi, “Ira ọdaak man bi, awobha ttara man maa, mọwọhn ovu-nwa ọnang-ọ.”
\p 
\v 16 Oreng-eden nwa kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi obhina bi, “Kaambi abọkh-m ahok ma, kaam ọchattọhk fabọng manda vani kínchi. Yina, idikha asi ẹnanga ẹkwọmichẹ, tzọkha chẹ anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi.” (Wa Manoa kotzini bi, orenga-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi wọ.)
\p 
\v 17 Iwa Manoa ọbọbh oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi bi, “Kọ akpen yan o, ifha mọfha ọnang-ọ ikpokpobha k'ogbe kw'atzim pọ ákhaama ẹjaakhi k'odik-ọkka?”
\p 
\v 18 Oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi obhina bi, “Ira kaam che chaam kabọbh e, okhuri bi, kwẹ kọ kọttaan e.”
\v 19 Wa Manoa ọtzọkha ovu-nwa ọmaana ẹnanga ch'abọkpa, otzima osi ẹjafọhni k'itzakpa ebir-ebir ọnang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi. Wa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi osi okkokkoni-dik m'itzitzikha sa Manoa ọmaana kwanọng kwẹ:
\v 20 Mada akpondaak awọm k'ijafọhnibe achina k'ẹrọng, oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi orenga m'akpongdaak mba ofona. Mada Manoa ọmaana kwanọng kwẹ are odik nwa, bẹ atto akhubha otzitzikha fabẹ k'irerek.
\v 21 Mada oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi oni Manoa ọmaana kwanọng kwẹ abẹ dọk oyini, Manoa on-otzin bi, oreng-eden kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi wọ.
\p 
\v 22 Manoa oben kwanọng kwẹ bi, “Mọkk'ọpa ma e, mokk'Ibinọkpaabyi ọra e!”
\p 
\v 23 Mẹ wọ ofon, kwanọng kwẹ obhina bi, “Idikha ira Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọkhami bi ofhu man, ira ẹnanga ẹkwọmichẹ chaman ọmaana ẹnanga chaman ch'abọkpa cha mosi, kọtzọkha. Ira man idik nna biphyir kọkhọhkha, man sẹ ọgbaak-gbaak kobiro ọgbaak.”
\p 
\v 24 Iwa kwanọng nwa okwu ọmaan nwa kw'ijinọng, ọkpẹ-ẹ Samson. Wa nnwa nwa ọbar, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọdẹ-ẹ.
\v 25 Wa egwugwuma ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ch'ẹfa ẹnwẹ-ẹ mada owobh ka Mahane-Dan, k'ottem kwa Zora ttara Ẹshtaol.
\c 14
\s1 Ọbada kwa Samson
\p 
\v 1 Iwa Samson ofona ochina ka Timna, ọtza ore ominanwa wani kw'ofon Philistiya.
\v 2 Mada okhun e, ọtza ọgbaak otte ttara ọkka bi, “Kaam nkk'oPhilistiya-minanwa nna ka Timna; bọng dọkh-ẹ anang-m, ode kwanọng kwaam.”
\p 
\v 3 Otte ttara ọkka abhina bi, “Ode bi da aminava akkakka anade k'echimma chọ, obiro ode k'ottem kw'anọng paman biphyir wọ raa, kwa kọ akhaambi achina k'anọng pa Philistiya p'ani ọkpakkọrikkọ asi bi, atza atzọkha kwanọng o?”
\p Kaambi mẹ wọ, Samson oben otte bi, “Kẹ wọ ode ọnọng kw'ọdaakh-m e. Kọ tzọkh-ẹ anang-m mba.”
\v 4 (Wa otte ttara ọkka karong bi, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi wọ obeni bi, orenga mẹ ọnang anọng pa Philistiya ettuma; okhuri bi, iwa anọng p'Israẹl awobh k'irekhirek kw'anọng pa Philistiya.)
\p 
\v 5 Mando kwa Samson otzim otte ttara ọkka afona achina k'obhon kwa Timna. Mada bẹ apyiri k'iwoni sa grep k'obhon kwa Timna, ekye eyin mẹ em-esi amọng erenga etzor Samson ka for.
\v 6 Wa egwugwuma ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ch'ẹfa ẹnwa Samson ẹnang-ẹ ẹfa, ch'otzim mbọhk-mbohk ọbọkha ekye ọjaakhi, mach'ira ọjaakhi ovu-nwa. Yina, wa ọkka ttara otte odik kw'ọkk'ọsa kọgbaakhi.
\v 7 Ofona ọtza okhebha kwanọng nwa ka Timna ọgbaakh-ẹ atzim, ọkhaama idadaakha ọmaan-ẹ.
\p 
\v 8 Mada ọn-ọkpa nnam k'ogbe ọdọdọk bi, ọtza ọtzọkha ominanwa nwa k'ọbada, otzini chen okkeri kẹ da okye-bukhi oyim, on-ore akhọkhọna ọmaana akhọkhọnana k'okye-bukhi ẹtzaanga.
\v 9 Mando kwa onemi ọbọhk ọgwọhngi akhọkhọnana ọttaakhi, da om-orenga ofona. Mada ofon ọtza okhebha otte ttara ọkka, ọtzọkha akhọkhọhnana ọnang bẹ, bẹ attaakhi. Yina, wa bẹ kọgbaakhi bi, okk'akhọkhọnana ọgwọhngi k'okye-bukhi nwa.
\p 
\v 10 Iwa otte ọtzọn-ẹ abẹ, bẹ atza k'ominanwa nwa. Samson osi ọdadaami kw'ọbada, otzor k'ẹmmaana ch'adikkobh.
\v 11 Mada anọng pa Philistiya arẹ-ẹ, bẹ atzekha adikkobh anọng ẹrọbh obhiri jobh anang-ẹ mach'ayokh-ẹkhaan pẹ.
\p 
\v 12 Iwa Samson oben bẹ bi “Tte ntta bọng odem. Idikha bọng anang-m ẹjaakhi ch'odem nwa m'iwu nna izenamfa s'ọdadaami nwa, kaam nnang bọng anọhma-baba ẹrọbh obhiri jobh pa bẹ atzim ndik ọkkakka asi, ọmaana abara-ho ẹrọbh obhiri jobh.
\v 13 Idikha bọng an'aam ebhina afha anang, bọng akhaambi anang-m anọhma-baba ẹrọbh obhiri jobh pa bẹ atzim ndik ọkkakka asi, ọmaana abara-ho ẹrọbh obhiri jobh.”
\p Adikkobh mba abhina bi, “Tte moyonga itzọhng atta man odem kwọ.”
\p 
\v 14 Obhina oben bi,
\q1 “Ọchattọhk ofon k'ọnọng kw'ochi ọttọhk;
\q2 Idadaama ifon k'ọnọng kw'ọkhaam ẹfa.”
\m K'iwu ittaan, bẹ ebhina ch'odem nwa kafha anang.
\p 
\v 15 Ottong iwu inna, anọng mba atza aben kwanọng kwa Samson bi, “Bọhra odim ọgbaak man odem kw'odem kwẹ oyini, oni mando ode mọkwọm-ọ ttara ẹhọhmmọr ch'atte biphyir k'ekpon. Bọng abheri man ma bi, bọng akwu afhu ekpo pyaman o?”
\p 
\v 16 Mando kwa kwanọng kwa Samson otto ọbang-ẹ ma for, obhom oben bi, “Kọ kindaakhi! Idadaakha mebubuni kakhaam ttar-m. Akk'anọng paam odem atta, yina, kaam ẹjaakhi ch'odem nwa kagbaakhi.”
\p Samson obhina bi, “Kaambi otte ttara ọkka kwaam wọ, bẹ ndimi mgbaakha, okhuri yan kw'ira mgbaakh-ọ ọ?”
\v 17 Wa obhom ẹmọng m'iwu nna izanamfa biphyir s'ọdadaami. Ottong iwu izenamfa nnuma, Samson e, ọgbaakh-ẹ odem kw'odem nwa oyini, okhuri da ochin ororo ọgban-ẹ. Mando kwa ominanwa nwa ọbhakhi osi ẹjaakhi ch'odem nwa, ọnang anọng pẹ.
\p 
\v 18 Yina ẹchọhkha etto m'ewu ch'ettong izenamfa, ajinọng p'obhon nwa aben Samson bi,
\q1 “Mbọng vọ ọdaami ọyọhnga akhọkhọnana o?
\q2 Mbọng vọ ọkhaam ẹfa ọyọhnga ekye o?”
\p Samson on-oben bẹ bi,
\q1 “Idikha ira bọng ani kwanọng kwaam abọk k'ẹfa,
\q2 ira ọnọng kw'ọkhaama ẹjaakhi ch'odem kwaam, kode.”
\p 
\v 19 Mẹ wọ ofon, egwugwuma ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ch'ẹfa ẹnwa Samson. Ofona ọhakha k'Ashkẹlọn, ọtza ofhu ajinọng pabẹ ẹrọbh obhiri jobh, ọwọra bẹ ekpo biphyir ọtzọkha pyẹ ọtza ọnang ajinọng mbuma p'anang-ẹ ẹjaakhi ch'odem nwa. Wa otzima idọdọkhi ọkpa nnam ọbhana k'otte k'ọhọhm.
\v 20 Iwa bẹ atzọkha kwanọng kwa Samson anang odikkobh wani m'ottem kw'ayokh-ẹkhaan p'iwa asi ọdadaami kw'ọbada kwa Samson.
\c 15
\s1 Samson okhem anọng pa Philistiya
\p 
\v 1 K'ogbe mẹ, m'ọphagbe kwa wit, wa Samson otzima ovu-nwa bi, ọtza odibh kwanọng kwẹ. Oben bi, “Kaam nchin k'ẹmaanggọ cha kwanọng kwaam.” Yina, wa otte kwa kwanọng kokher bi, ndim k'ẹtzaanga.
\p 
\v 2 Iwa otte kwa kwanọng oben bi, “Kaam iwa nnong kẹ bi, ominanwa nwa kọ kọdaakhi, kẹ wọ osi, ndọkh-ẹ nnang oyokh-ẹkhaan wani kwọ. Ọgbaanọkka kw'ikhakhari k'ojibhi ọyọhng-ẹ o? Kọ tzọkha oyok nwuma.”
\p 
\v 3 Iwa Samson oben bẹ bi, “Ogbe nwa, oponga-pyibha kindọkha k'odik kwa ńsi anọng pa Philistiya; Kaam ńsi bẹ itzama ọkhaam-ọkhaam.”
\v 4 Mando kw'ofon ọtza ọbọkha azizi arọbh chi, ọtzọkha bẹ ọdabh afa-afa ka nsara. Ọn-ọtzọkha ikhebh ọdabh ka nsara mfa kpenamkpen.
\v 5 Ọtzọkha okhebh mva oyeni, yina on-otte azizi mba ọbọhk k'iwoni s'awit s'anọng pa Philistiya. Ọkwọmi awit pa bẹ aye-oye ọmaana p'atzima abe k'iwoni, ọmaana iwoni sa grep ttara iwoni s'oliv.
\p 
\v 6 K'ogbe kw'anọng pa Philistiya an-abọbhi bi, “Anyi wọ osi odik nwa?” Bẹ agbaak bẹ bi, “Samson kw'ode ọnyẹ kw'ojinọng kw'ofon Timnit wọ osi odik nwa e, okhuri da bẹ atzọk kwanọng kwẹ anang oyok-ẹkhaan kwẹ e.”
\p Mando kw'anọng pa Philistiya afon atza akwọmi ominanwa nwa ọmaana otte maa, bẹ ape.
\v 7 Samson oben bẹ bi, “Mada bọng an-asi manda, kaam nchekhi bi, ọwọhng kinkwokha maa ndukha odik kwa bọng asi.”
\v 8 Wa otzima ittem-dọkhiji orima bẹ abẹ, ofhu bẹ k'ọhaabh. Obina ọtza owobha k'ọmma-kw'itzakpa kw'Etam.
\p 
\v 9 Iwa anọng pa Philistiya atza abhing ka Juda, bẹ anyaami apyiri ka Lehi.
\v 10 Wa anọng pa Juda an-abọbh bi, “Okhuri yan kwa bọng akwu arima man abẹ?”
\p Bẹ abhina bi, “M'ọkk'ọkwa bi, okwu ọbọkha Samson ọtza ọkhe mgbakkọhbh e, mọsẹ-ẹ odik kw'osi man.”
\p 
\v 11 Mẹ wọ ofon, anọng pa Juda nnọhna nzenamfa obhiri arọbh jobh, ahakha k'ọmma-kw'itzakpa kw'Etam atza aben Samson bi, “Ode bi kọ katzini bi, mowobh k'irekhirek kw'anọng pa Philistiya? Bọng odik kw'asi man ma o?”
\p Obhina bi, “Kaam nginggẹ ndukha odik kwa bẹ asi-m e.”
\p 
\v 12 Mẹ wọ ofon, bẹ aben-ẹ bi, “Mọkk'ọkwa bi, okwu ọdabh-ọ, mọtzọkh-ọ ọnang anọng pa Philistiya.”
\p Samson oben bi, “Bọng chekhi anang-m bi, bọbọng ọkhaam arang afhu-m.”
\p 
\v 13 Bẹ abhina bi, “Mokk'okhera. Man kọ kofhu, mokhinggẹ ọdabh-ọ, ọtzọkh-ọ ọnang bẹ.” Mando kwa bẹ atzim ndik mmasẹ mfa adabh-ẹ, atzima ayin k'itzakpa.
\v 14 Mada opyiri ka Lehi, anọng pa Philistiya am-awuri amọng arenga atzor-ẹ. Mando kw'egwugwuma ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ẹhak ẹnwẹ-ẹ, ẹnang-ẹ ẹfa. Ndik sa bẹ adabh-ẹ ka mbọhk, ikpaara mach'adik-bukhi p'ekpon ẹkwọmi, ichaar-ẹ ka mbọhk.
\v 15 Mando kw'odungi ọkhọbhi kw'agba p'ẹnyanyaang kw'ore mẹ, ọtzim-ẹ ofhu anọng nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh jobh.
\p 
\v 16 Mẹ wọ ofon, Samson oben bi,
\q1 “Kaam nkk'ọkhọbhi kw'agba p'ẹnyanyaang
\q2 ndima nsi bẹ ade macha nnyanyaang.
\q1 Kaam nkk'ọkhọbhi kw'agba p'ẹnyanyaang
\q2 ndima mfhu ajinọng nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh jobh.”
\m 
\v 17 Mada okyer atzim mba ọgbagbaak, ọbhari ọkhọbhi nwa kw'agba p'ẹnyanyaang; wa bẹ ayeri ibe nna Ramat-Lehi.
\p 
\v 18 Iwa ofon da asi akk'ẹ adaakha kpọng, obhom oyeri Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, oben bi, “Kọ akk'kaam ọtzọhmnọng kwọ ekhema ch'ideden ananga. Ma, kaam nna nnenga isi-dadaakha abẹ, nda mpe ka mbọhk anọng p'ani ọkpakkọrikkọ asi o?”
\v 19 Wa Ibinọkpaabyi osi asi amaam ayin k'ọmma k'eje ch'okwung k'irerek sa Lehi. Mada Samson ogwo asi mba, ẹfa ewobh-ẹ obiro ogwengi. Mẹ wọ ofon, bẹ ayeri okhekhaho nwa Ẹn-Hakore, kw'ọtzim owobh ka Lehi maa, apyiri ma.
\p 
\v 20 Iwa Samson ode osi-aponga k'Israẹl ka cho ẹrọbh, k'ogbe kw'iwa anọng pa Philistiya adabhi bẹ.
\c 16
\s1 Samson ọmaana Delila
\p 
\v 1 Iwa ewu dani, Samson ofona ochina k'obhon kwa Gaza k'ẹkhọma cha Philistiya. Mada owobh kẹ, ọtza obhing k'ọzaaza-kwanọng wani m'erungiwu nduma.
\v 2 Wa bẹ agbaak anọng pa Gaza bi, Samson owobh ma e. Mando kw'anọng pa Gaza afon atza ayeri ajinọng atzobha, bẹ ayima ka mbaakhamma s'obhon m'erungiwu nduma biphyir, atzik. Bẹ awobha \it bi sẹbh\it* m'erungiwu nduma, am-aben ayok bi, “Mọ́fhẹ-ẹ da ewu ekk'ehobha.”
\p 
\v 3 Yina, wa Samson oyima mẹ maa, opyiri k'orungittem. Obina m'orungittem ọtza ọbọkha mbaakhamma s'obhon mọgbakha mkpọmmachi mfa ọkhọbhi, okwu ọttara k'agbọkhọrọ ttara ekpo pya mbaakhamma biphyir. Otzini pyẹ ọnana ka mbabaang otzima ovura k'egbegbeho ebir-ebir, k'okhubha kw'okkeri Hẹbrọn itzitzikha.
\p 
\v 4 K'ogbe mẹ, wa kwanọng wani kw'okpen Delila okwu ọdaak Samson k'Ittolim sa Sorẹk.
\v 5 Wa adabhi p'anọng pa Philistiya atza akhebha kwanọng nwa aben-ẹ bi, “Bọhra Samson ifha ọgbaakh-ọ ndubhama kw'ẹfa chẹ, ifha mọfha ọnẹ-ẹ ẹfa, mobiro ọfha ọdabh-ẹ ndik, mokhem-ẹ. Ọnọng-ọnọng mottem kwaman, ọnang-ọ ashẹkẹl pa silva nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh chi.”
\p 
\v 6 Mando kwa Delila ọtza oben Samson bi, “Gbaakh-m ndubhama s'ẹfa chọ, ọmaana odem kw'ọnọng ọfha ọdabh-ọ ndik otzima okhem-ọ.”
\p 
\v 7 Samson obhin-ẹ bi, “Idikha ọnọng manda wani otzim adik-naanga azenamfa p'agwu-ogwu ọdabh-m, kaam ẹfa ẹhaam-ọha mach'ẹha ojinọng kpenamkpen.”
\p 
\v 8 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa adabhi p'anọng pa Philistiya achena kwanọng nwa adik-naanga azenamfa p'agwu-ogwu, otzima sẹ ọdabh-ẹ.
\v 9 Ode ch'ajinọng akk'akwa achubha m'ẹmaanggọ. Kwanọng nwa oyer-ẹ, “Samson, anọng pa Philistiya an-abọkh-ọ e!” Mando kw'ọbọk adik-naanga mba ọkpaara \it bi pọhbh\it* mach'edik-naanga eyon da ẹbaang ekpon. Iwa bẹ ndubhama s'ẹfa chẹ kafha aronga.
\p 
\v 10 Iwa Delila oben Samson bi, “Akk'asa nger odidinginọng, akk'aam ibhora asa. Kọ gbaakh-m odem kw'ọnọng ọfha orenga ọdabh-ọ.”
\p 
\v 11 Oben bi, “Idikha ọnọng otzim ndik mmasẹ sa bẹ anatzima am-atzima, kaam ẹfa ẹhaam-ọha mach'ẹha ojinọng kpenamkpen.”
\p 
\v 12 Mando kwa Delila ọtzọk ndik mmasẹ otzima ọdabh-ẹ. Ode ch'ajinọng akk'akwa achubha m'ẹmaanggọ. Kwanọng nwa oyer-ẹ, “Samson, anọng pa Philistiya an-abọkh-ọ e!” Mando kw'ọbọk ndik sa bẹ adabh-ẹ ka mbọhk ọkpaara, mach'adik-naanga p'an-akkọri.
\p 
\v 13 Iwa Delila oben Samson bi, “Kọ atzim am-asi-m nger odidinginọng o, akk'aam ibhora asa. Kọ gbaak-m odem kw'ọnọng ọfha orenga ọdabh-ọ.”
\p Samson obhina bi, “Idikha atzọk akpadim mba p'eho chaam azenamfa, atzima edik-naanga abọkha bẹ abira atzima akpak atzobha bẹ, kaam ẹfa ẹhaam-ọha mach'ẹha ojinọng kpenamkpen.” Mẹ wọ ofon, mada Samson ọm-ọttaabha ọda, Delila ọtzọkha akpadim azenamfa p'eho cha Samson, ọbọkha bẹ
\v 14 obiro otzima akpak otzobha bẹ.
\p Mando kwobiro oyer-ẹ, “Samson, anọng pa Philistiya an-abọkh-ọ e!” Mando kw'ọphyọbh k'ọda, ọrọbha akpak obiro ọchaari edik-naanga ch'ẹbọk akpadim etzobha.
\p 
\v 15 Mẹ wọ ofon, Delila oben-ẹ bi, “Ka yan kwa kọ aben bi, ‘Kaam ndaakh-ọ ọdaak,’ kw'an-akher ajaakhi ndubhama kwọ anang-m? On-ode igbe ittaan ma s'akk'asa nger odidinginọng, kakher ajaakhi ndubhama s'ẹfa chọ anang-m.”
\v 16 Wa Samson e, ettem ebhem-ẹ itzama-itzama, okhuri odem kwa Delila oreng ọyaakh-ẹ atzim k'ewu kpenamkpen.
\p 
\v 17 Ofona mẹ, wa ọgbaakh-ẹ odik kpenamkpen oben bi, “Ẹkpẹr kaam k'eho etzim ẹm-ẹttọhmi, kaam nde nnwa kwa bẹ atte ọbọhk ttẹwọr k'ibhọr anang Ibinọkpaabyi. Idikha bẹ aphyir-m isisaa, kaam ẹfa ẹhaam-ọha mach'ẹha ojinọng kpenamkpen.”
\p 
\v 18 Mada Delila ore bi, Samson ọkk'ẹ odik kpenamkpen ọgbaakha, ọtzọhm ẹkkaabha ọnaang adabhi pa Philistiya oben bi, “Bọng na kpa nnam m'ogbe nwa; kkeri ọkk'aam odik kpenamkpen ọgbaakha.” Mando kw'adabhi pa Philistiya atzim silva ka mbọhk akwu.
\v 19 Mada ọbọkh-ẹ ọttaabh-ẹ ma ndaak, Delila oyeri ọnọng okwu ophyiri Samson akpadim azenamfa pẹ, ọsi ẹfa ẹhẹ-ẹ.
\p 
\v 20 Mẹ wọ ofon, kwanọng nwa oyer-ẹ, “Samson, anọng pa Philistiya an-abọkh-ọ e!”
\p Mada ọphyọbh, ochibhi bi, “Tte nsi macha mminsi, mkpaara ndik sabẹ atzima adabh-m.” Yina, wa korong bi, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọkk'ẹ ọbọhk ọtta.
\p 
\v 21 Mando kw'anọng pa Philistiya abọkh-ẹ, arọbh-ẹ chen, atzim-ẹ achina k'obhon kwa Gaza. Wa bẹ agbaakh-ẹ ttara mgbakkọhbh sa brons, bẹ ahokh-ẹ bi, om-okhok ekpo k'ẹgbakkọhbh-ttọhmma.
\v 22 Yina, wa isisaa sẹ s'eho ibiri ittẹwọr imen.
\s1 Obo kwa Samson
\p 
\v 23 Iwa adabhi pa Philistiya atzobha bi, bẹ afọhni ẹja ọkkakka anang Dagọn kw'ode ọkha fabẹ, ttara bi, bẹ abira asi ọdadaami, bẹ aben bi, “Ọkha faman okk'Samson kw'ode ọttattaanga-nọng kwaman, ọtzọkha okhe man ka mbọhk.”
\p 
\v 24 Mada anọng mba arẹ-ẹ, bẹ anang ọkha fabẹ ikpokpobha, aben bi,
\q1 “Ọkha famaan
\q2 okk'ọttattaanga-nọng kwaman ọtzọkha okhe man ka mbọhk,
\q1 kw'okhe irerek saman ka dama-dama
\q2 obiro ofhu man k'ọhaabh.”
\p 
\v 25 Mada bẹ am-asi ọdadaami, bẹ aben bi, “Bọng dima Samson ayin ka, okwu osi mọmma aha.” Wa bẹ ayeri Samson k'ẹgbakkọhbh-ttọhmma oyin ka, okwu osi bẹ amma aha.
\p Mada bẹ abẹ-ẹ k'ottem kwa mkpọmmachi.
\v 26 Wa Samson oben ọtzọhmnọng kw'ọbọkh-ẹ bi, “Tte mbe k'ibe sa mfha mbọkha mbọhk ka mkpọmmachi sa mbọk ọhọhm nwa, ifha mphe mẹ.”
\v 27 Wa anọng afu m'ọhọhm nwa \it bi pyẹr\it*, ajinọng ọmaana panọng; wa adabhi pa Philistiya abira awobha mẹ, anọng nnọhna nzenamfa obhiri arọbh jobh ajinọng ọmaana panọng, awobha k'ẹnyọhng am-are idik sa Samson om-osi.
\v 28 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa Samson ozi njọhm oyeri Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, oben bi, “O Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi kw'Ọyọhng, jim-m e. Tzotzokhaan, Ibinọkpaabyi nang-m ẹfa ogbe nwa wani dokh e, ndima ẹbọhk-duk dani ndima ndukha chen paam afa p'anọng mba pa Philistiya arọbh.”
\v 29 Mando kwa Samson ọbọk mbọhk ka mkpọmmachi mfa sa mbọk ọhọhm nwa k'ottem. Ọbọkha odimbọhk k'ẹkpọmmachi dani, obiro otzima kwabọhk ọbọkha ndonggo.
\v 30 Samson oben bi, “Tte kaam mpe ttara anọng mba pa Philistiya!” Mẹ wọ ofon, Samson otzima ẹfa chẹ biphyir onyuni mkpọmmachi nna maa, wa ọhọhm otto ọkpẹkhi adabhi pa Philistiya ọmaana anọng biphyir p'awobh k'ọhọhm nwa k'ẹtzaanga. Wa anọng p'ofhu k'ogbe kw'ope, an-anyọhnga anọng p'ofhu da orukhi akpen.
\p 
\v 31 Iwa agbaanatte pẹ, ọmaana ẹhọhmmọr ch'otte biphyir afona bi, atza atzọkh-ẹ. Bẹ atzim-ẹ akpa nnam atza anọhnga k'ottem kwa Zora ọmaana Ẹshtaol k'epekhubh ch'otte Manoa. Kẹ wa ode osi-aponga k'Israẹl ka cho ẹrọbh.
\c 17
\s1 Ọkha fa Mika okpobh
\p 
\v 1 Iwa ojinọng wani kw'ofon k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim, kw'okpen Mika,
\v 2 obeni ọkka bi, “Ashekẹl pa silva nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh chi pa bẹ atzọk ka mbọhk sọ, pa areng abẹ anang ọnọng kw'ọtzọk ẹmma, pa mbiri mmaanga da agbaakhi okhuri, kkeri bẹ ma e, kaam wọ ndọk bẹ e.”
\p Ọkka on-oben bi, “Nnwa kwaam, tte Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọdọ-ọ!”
\p 
\v 3 Mada orikhi ashekẹl mba pa silva nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh chi ọnang ọkka, ọkka on-oben bi, “K'odik-ọkka, kaam ntte asilva mba paam ọbọhk nnang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, ifha nnwa kwaam osi ọgbatza kwa bẹ atzima silva abhọri. Kaam ńdọkha ọgbatza nwa mkpa nnam nnang-ọ.”
\p 
\v 4 Mada orikhi asilva mba ọnang ọkka, ọkka ọn-ọtzọkha ashẹkẹl arọbh jobh pa silva ọnang otzetzekha kwa silva, kw'otzim bẹ oduk ọgbatza nwa. Wa bẹ atzọkh-ẹ atza ahok k'ọhọhm kwa Mika.
\p 
\v 5 Iwa ojinọng nwa kw'okpen Mika okkekkeni ọkhaama ọkhapa, wa osi ẹphọd ọmaana ikha sa ẹhọhmmọr, okwu ọtzọkha nnwa wani kwẹ kw'ijinọng, otzima osi ọfọhnẹja kwẹ.
\v 6 K'ogbe nwa, wa anọng p'Israẹl ọvaarnọng kakhaam, wa ọnọng kpenamkpen orukhi akpen p'adaakh-ẹ.
\p 
\v 7 Iwa odikkobh kw'efonamma cha Lẹvi, ka Bẹtẹlẹhẹm k'ẹkhọma cha Juda,
\v 8 obina oji Bẹtẹlẹhẹm ka Juda oror ibe idọdọk s'owobha. Mada oreng k'eden, ọtza ọyaakha k'ọhọhm kwa Mika, k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim.
\p 
\v 9 Mika ọbọbh-ẹ bi, “Kọ afon man o?”
\p Oben bi, “Kaam mfon k'efonamma cha Lẹvi, ka Bẹtẹlẹhẹm k'ẹkhọma cha Juda e. Kaam nnori ibe sa nwobha.”
\p 
\v 10 Mẹ wọ ofon, Mika oben-ẹ bi, “Kọ ruk ma ttar-m, ifha ade otte ọmaana ọfọhnẹja kwaam. Kaam ńnang-ọ ashẹkẹl jobh pa silva ka cho, mbiri nnang-ọ ọbara ttara ọchattọhk.” Ojinọng nwa kw'efonamma cha Lẹvi odim k'ẹtzaanga.
\v 11 Wa odikkobh nwa kwa Lẹvi okhera bi, oruk ttar-ẹ. Odikkobh nwa on-ode macha nnwa wani kwẹ kw'ijinọng.
\v 12 Mando kwa Mika osi odikkobh nwa kwa Lẹvi ọfọhnẹja kwẹ, obiro oruk k'ọhọhm kwẹ.
\v 13 Mika e, oben bi, “Kaam nkk'nna nnonga bi, Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ósi ejibha osi ọnang-m, da odikkobh nwa kwa Lẹvi ọkk'ọfọhnẹja kwaam ọn-ọda.”
\c 18
\s1 Anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Dan arukhi ka Laish
\p 
\v 1 K'ogbe nwuma wa anọng p'Israẹl ọvaarnọng kakhaam.
\p K'ogbe nwuma wa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Dan am-aror ibe s'íde sabẹ, ifha bẹ afha aruk, okhuri da iwa bẹ ani ibe sa ide ekkema chabẹ atzima akhaama k'ottem kwa ngọma s'Israẹl.
\v 2 Mẹ wọ ofon, anọng pa Dan atzọhm akkakkaama pabẹ anọng azen p'afon k'ibhon sa Zora ọmaana Ẹshtaol bi, bẹ atza arom ẹkhọma nda bẹ abira arenga are chẹ. Wa ajinọng mba afon ka nnọmma sa Dan biphyir. Bẹ agbaak bẹ bi, “Bọng nọhng atza arenga are ẹkhọma nduma.”
\p Mando kw'ajinọng mba afon atza adim k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim atza ahakha k'ọhọhm kwa Mika, bẹ abhing mẹ m'erungiwu nduma.
\v 3 Mada bẹ abaang ọhọhm kwa Mika, bẹ atzin odikkobh kw'efonamma cha Lẹvi k'ẹmọng; mẹ wọ ofon, bẹ afona atza akhebh-ẹ, abọbh-ẹ bi, “Anyi wọ otzim-ọ akwu ma? Am-asi mbọng m'ibe nna? Mbọng vọ otzim-ọ okwu ma?”
\p 
\v 4 Mando kw'ọtzọk odik kwa Mika ọkk'ọsa ọnang-ẹ ọgbaak bẹ, oben bi, “Kẹ ọkk'aam ọtzọkha k'ọtzọhm e, kaam wọ nde ọfọhnẹja kwẹ e.”
\p 
\v 5 Mẹ wọ ofon, bẹ aben-ẹ bi, “Tzotzokhaan, kọ dọhn Ibinọkpaabyi ifha moronga s'ode na orenga kwaman ójibh ọnang man.”
\p 
\v 6 Ọfọhnẹja nwa obhina bẹ bi, “Bọng nọhng k'odidiri. Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi okk'orenga kwabọng ọda.”
\p 
\v 7 Mando kw'ajinọng mba azen abin achina Laish, atza are bi, anọng p'arukhi kẹ, bẹ arukhi k'odidiri, mach'anọng pa Sidọn, p'arukhi k'odidiri bẹ ojora kabira akhaama. Wa ojibhi anọng mba ojibh okhuri da ọttọhk manda vani oni k'ẹkhọma chabẹ owori. Ibe sa bẹ abira aruk ibhir eden k'ẹkhọma cha Sidọn, wa bẹ oforgbakha manda wani kakhaam ttara anọng adọdọk.
\p 
\v 8 Mada bẹ akhun k'ibhon sa Zora, ọmaana Ẹshtaol, votte abọbh bẹ bi, “Yan wọ kw'idik ide ttara bọng?”
\p 
\v 9 Bẹ abhina bi, “Bọng kwu, mọtza orima bẹ abẹ! Kkeri mọkk'ọra bi, irerek nnuma ijibh-ojibh. Bọng \it bi sẹbh\it* kawobha, bọng ogbe kakhibhi, mofona mọtza ọtzọkha irerek nnuma.
\v 10 Mada bọng apyiri kẹ, bọng akhebha anọng p'arukhi m'irerek nnuma p'ani chen ahokhi bi, odik ọfha otto. Ibe nna ide irerek s'iwoni-owoni s'Ibinọkpaabyi ọkk'ọtzọkha okhe bọng ka mbọhk, sẹ ide irerek s'ini ọttọhk manda vani iwori.”
\p 
\v 11 Mando kw'ajinọng ẹnọhna obhiri arọbh jobh p'afon k'ẹkhọma cha Dan ado for s'egbong, abina ka Zora, ọmaana Ẹshtaol.
\v 12 Mada bẹ areng ka ọkkadeden, bẹ attima ibhingabẹ abaanga Kiriyat-Jearim ka Juda. Kẹ wọ osi, bẹ ayeri okhubha kw'ewuchen em-edimi ka Kiriyat-Jẹrim Mahane-Dan maa, apyiri k'ewu cha mayina.
\v 13 Bẹ abina mẹ achina k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim, atza ahakha k'ọhọhm kwa Mika.
\p 
\v 14 Mẹ wọ ofon, ajinọng mba azen p'akk'ẹkhọma cha Laish atza aroma, abọbh votte pabẹ bi, “Bọng arong kẹ bi, ọhọhm wani k'ottem kw'ihọhm nna ọkhaam ẹphọd, ọmaana agbatza p'ẹhọhmmọr ọmaana ọgbatza kwa bẹ atzim silva abhọri? Bọbọng arong odem kwa bọng asi kẹ.”
\v 15 Mẹ wọ e, bẹ abina mẹ achina k'ọhọhm kwa Mika atza arima odikkobh kwa Lẹvi.
\v 16 Ajinọng mba ẹnọhna obhiri arọbh jobh p'efonamma cha Dan, p'akk'igbong-for adabha, atza abe k'ẹbaakhama ch'obhon.
\v 17 Ajinọng mba azen p'akk'afona atza arom irerek nna, adim k'ọhọhm ẹtzaanga atza atzini ọgbatza, ọmaana ẹphọd ọmaana agbatza p'ẹhọhmmọr, k'ogbe kw'ọfọhnẹja ọmaana ajinọng p'akk'igbong-for adabha anọng ẹnọhna obhiri arọbh jobh, abe k'ẹbaakhama ch'obhon.
\p 
\v 18 Mada ajinọng mba azen adimi k'ọhọhm kwa Mika atza atzọkha ọgbatza, ọmaana ẹphọd ọmaana agbatza p'ẹhọhmmọr, ọfọhnẹja ọbọbh bẹ bi, “Mbọng fa bọng am-asi?”
\p 
\v 19 Bẹ abhin-ẹ bi, “Myi \tl bi sẹẹbh! \tl* Odik ma kagbaak. Tzọn man abẹ, abira ade man otte ttara ọfọhnẹja. Bi kọ ade ọfọhnẹja k'ẹkhọma dani ọmaana k'ẹnọmma dani ch'Israẹl, ttara bi, kọ akwu ade ọfọhnẹja k'ẹhọhmmọr ch'ojinọng wani, yan wọ ojibhi ọtzam?”
\v 20 Wa ọfọhnẹja nwa ettem ẹdaam-ẹ k'eden-ọkka. Ọtzọkha ẹphọd ọmaana agbatza mba p'ẹhọhmmọr, ọmaana ọgbatza nwa kwa bẹ agwa-ọgwa, ọtzọn anọng mba abẹ ofona.
\v 21 Wa bẹ abhakhi nnam afona, va pabẹ ọmaana etzirakpo pyabẹ ttara ẹkhakhaama chabẹ, achi bẹ eden.
\p 
\v 22 Mada bẹ akk'afona k'odenmir aji ọhọhm kwa Mika, ajinọng p'arukhi abaanga Mika ayeri for sabẹ atzobha, bẹ afona atza akhọhbha anọng pa Dan k'itzitzikha.
\v 23 Mada bẹ agwoni bẹ, anọng pa Dan abhakhi nnam aben Mika bi, “Bọng odik wọ ọsọ-ọ kw'ayeri ajinọng pọ bi, bẹ akwu arima erima o?”
\p 
\v 24 Mika obhina bi, “Bọng atzọk agbatza pa ngwa, ọmaana ọfọhnẹja kwaam, atzima afona. Ọttọhk manda vani dọk kingaam, okhuri yan kwa bọng an-abọbh bi, “Kọ ode yan o?’ ”
\p 
\v 25 Anọng pa Dan abhina bi, “Ikhakhaanga kasi ttara man, oni mando ode, ajinọng bani ma, atzima ottem-pyibha arim-ọ abẹ, kọ ọmaana ẹhọhmmọr chọ ádimi akpen pabọng odimi.”
\v 26 Mando kw'anọng pa Dan afon \it bi bẹẹm\it*. Mada Mika ore bi, ajinọng mba agaangi ọtzam ayọhng-ẹ, ọbhakhi nnam ọbhana.
\p 
\v 27 Mando kwa bẹ atzọk ekpo pya Mika ọkk'ọsa, ọmaana ọfọhnẹja kwẹ atzima afona achina ka Laish, atza arima egbong ttara anọng p'arukhi k'odidiri bẹ ojora kabira akhaama. Bẹ atzima ọkkangkkaang arima anọng mba abẹ, bẹ abira akwọmi odedenmon kwabẹ.
\v 28 Wa ọnọng manda wani kw'ọkkaan bẹ kode, da obhon kwabẹ obhiri eden k'obhon kwa Sidọn, ttara bi, wa bẹ oforgbakha ttara obhon manda wani kakhaam. Wa odedenmon nwa owobh k'ittolim s'ibaang Bet-Rehob.
\p Wa anọng pa Dan an-abira asi odedenmon nwa, aruk mẹ.
\v 29 Kaambi ode bi, wa obhon nwa okpen Laish, bẹ an-akpẹ-ẹ che abhina Dan, kw'ode otte kwabẹ kw'ideden, kw'iwa ode nnwa kwa Jekọb.
\v 30 Wa anọng pa Dan atzọkha ọgbatza nwa attima, Jonatan kw'ode nnwa kwa Gershọm, kw'ode nnwa kwa Mosẹs, ọmaana va pẹ p'ijinọng bọ iwa ade afọhnẹja p'ẹkhọma cha Dan maa, akwu apyiri k'ogbe kwa bẹ abọk ẹkhọma nda k'ẹmmọri.
\v 31 Bẹ achina ororo akpobha ọgbatza nwa kwa Mika ọkk'ọsa, k'ogbe biphyir kw'ọhọhm kw'Ibinọkpaabyi owobh ka Shilo.
\c 19
\s1 Ofona-nwa kwa Lẹvi ọmaana ọkkọra-kwanọng kwẹ
\p 
\v 1 K'ogbe nwuma wa anọng p'Israẹl ọvaarnọng kakhaam.
\p Iwa ọkhaam ojinọng wani kw'efonamma cha Lẹvi, kw'orukhi k'ẹtzaanga-ẹtzaanga kw'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim, kw'ọtzọk ọkkọra-kwanọng kw'ofon Bẹtẹlẹhẹm ka Juda.
\v 2 Yina, wa ọkkọra-kwanọng nwa osi ẹmmaana-tzama otzima otzor odim. Wa obin oji odim, ọkpa nnam k'otte k'ọhọhm ka Bẹtẹlẹhẹm kwa Juda. Mada okk'aphe anna owobha kẹ,
\v 3 odim obina ttara atzọhmnọng pẹ ọmaana nnyanyaang sẹ mfa, bi ọtza okhukh-ẹ ọkpa nnam. Mando kwa kwanọng nwa otzim odim, ọnwa k'ọhọhm kw'otte. Mada otte kwa kwanọng ọrẹ-ẹ, ọgọm-ẹ ttara ottem-daamiji.
\v 4 Ọnyẹ kwẹ kw'ode otte kwa kwanọng, ophyem-ẹ bi obhing, mando kw'obhingi ttara bẹ k'iwu ittaan. Om-ochi obiro ogwo, obiro ọttaabha mẹ.
\p 
\v 5 Ottong iwu inna, bẹ abina k'ekpekpebha ado for bi, bẹ afona. Yina, otte kwa kwanọng oben odim kwa nnwa bi, “Kọ bọkha ẹbhọhr yina afona.”
\v 6 Mando kwa bẹ anọng afa awobh ibe rani achi ọchattọhk abira agwo atzuk. Mada bẹ akk'akyera, otte kwa kwanọng oben bi, “Tzotzokhaan, tte ettem ẹdaam-ọ bi, awobha ma m'erungiwu nda.”
\v 7 Yina, k'ogbe kw'ojinọng nwa obin bi ofona, otte kwa kwanọng oden-ẹ maa, okhera oyima m'erungiwu nduma.
\v 8 K'ekpebha ch'ewu ehobh, ch'ettong iwu izen, mada obin bi ofona, otte kwa kwanọng oben bi, “Kọ bọkha ẹbhọhr, awobha maa, apyiri k'ẹya!” Mando kwa bẹ atzọni achi ọttọhk.
\p 
\v 9 K'ogbe kw'ojinọng nwa, ọmaana ọkkọra-kwanọng kwẹ ttara ọtzọhmnọng kwẹ abin bi afona, ọnyẹ kwẹ kw'ode otte kwa kwanọng, oben bi, “Kker e, erungi en-ekkekkeni epyi e, chi ọttọhk yima ma e; kkeri ewu ẹkk'ẹha e. Iphyini ekpekpebha, abina abhana k'ọhọhm kwọ e.”
\v 10 Yina, wa itta nwa kẹ kọdaakhi bi obiro oyima mẹ k'erungiwu ẹdọdọk. Wa odo nnyanyaang sẹ ewobha, otzima ọkkọra-kwanọng kwẹ obina orenga ochina k'okhubha kwa Jẹbus (kw'ode Jẹrusalẹm).
\p 
\v 11 K'ogbe kwa bẹ akk'Jebus abaanga, da ewu en-ebubha, ọtzọhmnọng kw'ojinọng nwa oben itta kwẹ bi, “Tte mobhing m'odedenmon kw'anọng pa Jẹbus m'erungiwu nda e.”
\p 
\v 12 Itta kwẹ obhina ọtzọhmnọng nwa bi, “Mma e, man k'odedenmon manda wani kw'oni kw'anọng p'Israẹl ode kọ́tza. Ottu kw'am-osi mando, mọkwọbha óchina ka Gibea.
\v 13 Tte mokhonga opyiri ka Gibea, obiro ode Rama, ifha moyima m'obhon wani kw'ibhon nna ifa e.”
\v 14 Mando kwa be achin ororo maa, bẹ atza abaanga Gibea k'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin, ka nchọhkha-bọhk.
\v 15 Bẹ atza akwọbha ka Gibea bi bẹ abhing m'erungiwu nduma. Bẹ afona atza awobha ẹwọr ka nttaanga-chi s'odedenmon. Yina, ọnọng mando wani kw'oyeri bẹ bi, bẹ atza k'ọhọhm kwẹ kode.
\p 
\v 16 M'ẹchọhkha nduma, ọtzaminọng-jinọng wani kw'ofon k'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim, oruk ka Gibea ofona k'owoni kw'osi ọtzọhm okhuna. Wa anọng pa Gibea p'iwa arukhi m'ibe nna ade anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin.
\v 17 Mada ọtzaminọng nwa otzini chen okkeri ka nttaanga-chi s'odedenmon, ọn-ọbọbh bi, “Bọng afon man o? Bọng am-achina man o?”
\p 
\v 18 Ofona-nwa nwa kwa Lẹvi, obhina bi, “Mofon ka Bẹtẹlẹhẹm k'ẹkhọma cha Juda, om-ochina k'ẹtzaanga-ẹtzaanga kw'okhubha kwa mgbegbeho s'Ephraim, kẹ da kaam nnukhi. Wa kaam nda Bẹtẹlẹhẹm k'ẹkhọma cha Juda, ma, kaam nna nchin k'ọhọhm kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi. Ọnọng manda wani kw'ọkk'aam otzima bi, nda nyima k'ibe sẹ kode.
\v 19 Maman ọttọhk manda vani korori. Mọkhaam araraari-bukhi ọmaana ọchattọhk fa nnyanyaang saman ka e. Mọkhaama brẹd ọmaana atzuk p'abenga kaam ọmaana kwanọng kwaam ttara odikkobh nwa.”
\p 
\v 20 Mẹ wọ ofon, ọtzaminọng nwa oben bi, “Bọng kwu wobha k'ọhọhm kwaam. Bọng ma nttaanga-chi nna kàwobha. Tte nnang bọng ọttọhk kpenamkpen fa bọng aror.”
\v 21 Mando kw'ọtzaminọng nwa otzim ojinọng nwa ochina k'ọhọhm kwẹ, obiro ọnang nnyanyaang sẹ ọchattọhk. Mada okk'mando asa, bẹ agbobhi mmokpatzọkhi sabẹ, bẹ achi ọttọhk, abira agwo atzuk.
\p 
\v 22 K'ogbe kwa bẹ awobh k'ottemdamiji nwa, abibyanọng bani p'odedenmon nwa akhọri ọhọhm akhe k'ottem. Bẹ adani ọmma, am-akpẹbh ọtzaminọng kw'ọkhaam ọhọhm, aben bi, “Tzima ajinọng mba p'ahak m'ọhọhm kwọ kwu, ifha moyima bẹ abẹ.”
\p 
\v 23 Mando kw'ọkhaam-ọhọhm oyini k'iyaan, oben ajinọng mba bi, “Mma e, ab'ayi, bọng obibyadik-dema nwa kasi e. Mada ojinọng nwa ode okhekhennọng kwaam, bọng ogbarsa-dik-dema nwa, kàsi.
\v 24 Bọng kkeri, ominanwa kwaam ọmaana ọkkọra-kwanọng kw'ojinọng nwuma awobh ma e. Ńdima bẹ otzima nyin ka, ifha bọng ọtzọkha bẹ asi mach'achibhi pabọng ade. On-ode ojinọng nwa, bọng ogbarsa-dik-dema nwa kàsi.”
\p 
\v 25 Kaambi mẹ wọ, ajinọng mba itzọhng kayong anang ọtzaminọng nwa. Mẹ wọ ofon, ofona-jinọng nwa kwa Lẹvi, ọtzọkha ọkkọra-kwanọng kwẹ ọnang ajinọng mba k'iyaan. Bẹ abọkh-ẹ k'ẹfa ayima abẹ m'erungiwu nduma biphyir. Mada ewu ehobh, bẹ atte kwanọng ọbọhk ofona.
\v 26 M'owuhobha, kwanọng ọkpa nnam ochina k'ọhọhm kw'itta kwẹ om-owobha, otto owobha m'ibhokhi, oyima mẹ maa, ewu akyera ẹttaani.
\p 
\v 27 K'ogbe kw'itta kwa kwanọng nwa ọn-ọphyọbh k'ekpebha, okwunga ọmma bi ochina ororo k'orenga kwẹ, on-ore ọkkọra-kwanọng kwẹ kw'ọkk'ọtta m'ọmma kw'ọhọhm, ọtzọkha mbọhk ọbọkha m'ọmma.
\v 28 Itta kwẹ oben-ẹ bi, “Bina, mofona.” Yina, ẹmọng kosi. Mando kw'ojinọng nwa otzin-ẹ ọnana k'ẹnyanyaang otzim-ẹ ọbhana.
\p 
\v 29 Mada bẹ apyiri k'ọhọhm, ọtzọkha okkoro ọkpọhk kwanọng ka ngọma-ka ngọma k'obe jobh obhiri afa, ọtzọkha ọtzọhm ka ngọma jobh obhiri mfa s'Israẹl.
\v 30 Ọnọng kpenamkpen kw'ore kwẹ ọn-ọbhakhi oben oyok bi, “Bẹ odik-dema nwa atzim am-asa, anọng odik-dema nwa atzim am-ara, ttẹwọr k'ewu ch'iwa anọng p'Israẹl abin k'Ijip. Bọng chibhi odik nwa, mọkhaambi more odik okhuri kwẹ e!”
\c 20
\s1 Anọng p'Israẹl anangi anọng pa Bẹnjamin ettuma
\p 
\v 1 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl, ttẹwọr k'ẹkhọma cha Dan maa, apyiri ka Beershẹba, akwu attara ẹkhọma cha Gilead, afon atza atzobha mach'anọng bani ka Mizpa, k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi.
\v 2 Wa adenho biphyir pa ngọma s'anọng p'Israẹl atzọkha nwobha sabẹ, k'ewobha ch'anọng p'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi p'ade, anọng nnọhna-nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh jobh p'adabhi igbong-for atzim akkangkkaang.
\v 3 (Wa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin abhaanga bi, anọng p'Israẹl akk'avura atza atzobha ka Mizpa.) Mẹ wọ ọsi, anọng p'Israẹl aben bi, “Bọng gbaak man odem kw'obibya-dik-dema nwa oreng otto.”
\p 
\v 4 Mẹ wọ ofon, ojinọng nwa kw'efonamma cha Lẹvi, kw'ode odim kwa kwanọng kwa bẹ afhu, oben bi, “Kaam ọmaana ọkkọra-kwanọng kwaam wa mokwu ka Gibea k'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin bi, mobhing m'erungiwu nda.
\v 5 M'erungi nduma ajinọng p'afon ma Gibea akhubh-m, akwu akhọri ọhọhm akhe k'ottem, am-akham bi afhu-m. Bẹ ayima ọkkọra-kwanọng kwaam abẹ k'ẹfa maa, ope.
\v 6 Mẹ wọ osi, kaam ndọkha ọkkọra-kwanọng kwaam, njọhkhi k'akhuma-k'akhuma, ndọkha ikhuma rani-rani ndọhm k'ẹkhọma kpenamkpen ch'Israẹl akhaam ekkema, okhuri bi k'Israẹl wọ kwa bẹ awobh asi ebyibya nda ọmaana odik-ttama nwa.
\v 7 Mẹ wọ, bọbọng anọng p'Israẹl biphyir, bọng gbaakh-m odem kwa bọng akk'attọhna bi, asi e.”
\p 
\v 8 Mando kw'ajinọng biphyir atzim ochibhi wani abina k'ẹrọng, aben bi, “Ọnọng manda wani ka man k'ottem kw'ọbhana k'ọhọhm, kóde. K'odik-ọkka, ọnọng manda wani kw'ọbhana k'ọhọhm kwẹ, kóde.
\v 9 Ma wọ ode odik kwa mósi anọng pa Gibea: mọtza orima bẹ abẹ otzor k'odem kw'ẹjaakhi ch'ose, ede.
\v 10 Mọrọbha ajinọng jobh k'ottem kw'ajinọng arọbh azen k'ẹkhọma kpenamkpen ch'Israẹl. Mọrọbha ajinọng arọbh azen k'ottem kw'ajinọng nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh jobh kpenamkpen. Mọrọbha ajinọng nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh jobh, k'ottem kw'ajinọng nnọhna ẹrọbh obhiri nzen, ifha anọng mba am-aror ọchattọhk f'arim-egbong. K'ogbe kw'arim-egbong ápyiri ka Gibea k'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin, bẹ anang anọng pa Gibea ihem s'ibaan bẹ, k'odik-ttama nwa kwa bẹ asi k'Israẹl.”
\v 11 Mando kw'anọng p'Israẹl biphyir akhaam akhera dani mach'anọng bani, atza arima anọng p'odedenmon nwa abe.
\p 
\v 12 Iwa anọng pa ngọma s'anọng p'Israẹl atzọhm akkaabh-nkkaabha makhọra ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin, aben bi, “Bọng obibyadik-dem wọ kwa bọng asi k'ottem kwa bọng ma?
\v 13 Bọng nang man ajinọng-dama mba p'afon ka Gibea ifha mofhu bẹ, k'odem kwa mogbobhi ebibya nda k'Israẹl ọbhari.”
\p Yina, anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin bẹ ayokh-obhon p'Israẹl itzọhng kayong.
\v 14 Iwa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin abina k'ibhon sabẹ atza atzobha ka Gibea bi, bẹ arima anọng p'Israẹl abẹ.
\v 15 Mẹ ẹbaa mẹ, anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin atzekha ajinọng k'ibhon sabẹ p'am-atzima akkangkkaang arima egbong, anọng nnọhna arọbh attaan obhiri azen akwu attara k'adikkobh p'akhaam ẹfa abira aruk ka Gibea, anọng nnọhna-nnọhna nna obhiri arọbh azenamfa obhiri jobh.
\v 16 K'ottem kw'arim-egbong mba biphyir, wa bẹ atzek anọng ẹnọhna obhiri arọbh chi p'asi ibhiribọhk bẹ abira atzor ọbọhk k'ẹtzabhari. Ọnọng kw'ọm-obhari ọtza bi ọtzọbh ẹsisaa-naanga, kw'opyini kode.
\p 
\v 17 Akhiri anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin aji, wa anọng p'Israẹl atzobh anọng p'am-atzima ọkkangkkaang arima egbong, anọng nnọhna-nnọhna mfa obhiri arọbh jobh, bẹ biphyir akhaam ekkoji ch'egbong.
\p 
\v 18 Mẹ wọ ofon, wa anọng p'Israẹl afona achina ka Bẹtẹl atza adọhn Ibinọkpaabyi. Bẹ aben bi, “Bọng ẹkhọma k'ottem kwaman dọ echi eden ẹtza erima anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin abẹ o?”
\p Iwa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi obhina bi, “Ẹkhọma cha Juda dọ échi eden.”
\p 
\v 19 K'ekpebha ch'ewu ehobh mẹ, anọng p'Israẹl atza attima ibhingabe ọbaanga Gibea.
\v 20 Wa anọng p'Israẹl atza arima anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin abẹ, bẹ atza abe atzik bẹ ka Gibea.
\v 21 Wa anọng pa Bẹnjamin abina ka Gibea m'ewu nduma, atza afhu anọng p'Israẹl nnọhna arọbh afa obhiri chi, k'egbong-dam.
\v 22 Yina, wa anọng p'Israẹl an-akhe ayok ẹfa, abira atza abe atzik kẹ da iwa bẹ arim egbong k'echedenwu.
\v 23 Wa anọng p'Israẹl avura k'ikpokpobhabe atza abhom ayeri Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi maa, ẹchọhkha etto, Bẹ aben bi, “Mobiro ọ́tza orima anọng pa Bẹnjamin p'ade ayokh-obhon paman, abẹ o?”
\p Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi obhina bi, “Bọng nọhng atza arima bẹ abẹ.”
\p 
\v 24 Mando kw'anọng p'Israẹl arọkhi abaanga ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin, ottong iwu ifa.
\v 25 M'ogbe nwa, iwa ajinọng pa Bẹnjamin ayin ka Gibea akwu arima anọng p'Israẹl abẹ, bẹ afhu anọng p'Israẹl anọng nho nnọhna arọbh afa obhiri azen. Anọng pa bẹ afhu biphyir ade anọng p'am-atzima akkangkkaang arim egbong.
\p 
\v 26 Mẹ wọ ofon, anọng p'Israẹl biphyir ọmaana arim-egbong biphyir avura achina ka Bẹtẹl, atza awobha ẹwọr kẹ abhom anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi. Bẹ atzim ọchattọhk m'ewu nduma maa, apyiri k'ẹchọhkha. Bẹ asi nnanga nkwọmisẹ ọmaana nnanga s'odidiri anang Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi.
\v 27 Wa anọng p'Israẹl adọn Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi bi. (K'ogbe nwuma, wa Ẹkkọhbhi ch'Echekhi ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ewobh mẹ,
\v 28 Phinẹhas kw'ode nnwa kw'Eleaza, ọmaana nnwa kw'Aarọn kw'ijinọng bọ iwa ade atzọhmnọng mẹ). Wa bẹ abọbh bi, “Mobiro ọ́tza orima anọng pa Bẹnjamin p'ade ayokh-obhon paman, abẹ ra a?”
\p Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi obhina bi, “Bọng nọhng, kkeri ophyini ndọkha bẹ ọtzọkha nge bọng ka mbọhk.”
\p 
\v 29 Mẹ wọ ofon, anọng p'Israẹl atza abe akhọri Gibea.
\v 30 Wa anọng p'Israẹl avura atza arima ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin abẹ, ottong iwu ittaan. Bẹ atza abe atzik ka Gibea, mach'iwa bẹ akk'asa.
\v 31 Wa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin abina akwu arima anọng p'Israẹl abẹ, anọng p'Israẹl atzọr bẹ atzima abina k'odedenmon. Bẹ attẹwọr ammuma anọng p'Israẹl ekpo mach'iwa bẹ akk'am-asa maa, bẹ afhu ajinọng ẹrọbh obhiri jobh k'iwoni ọmaana k'akkadeden. Wa eden dani echin ka Bẹtẹl ndonggo echina ka Gibea.
\v 32 Mada anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin am-aben bi, “Mokhema bẹ okhema mach'ira k'echeden e.” Anọng p'Israẹl am-aben bi, “Bọng motzor bẹ otzima obina k'odedenmon oyin k'ọkkadeden.”
\p 
\v 33 Iwa ajinọng p'Israẹl biphyir abina k'obe f'ira bẹ abe, atza abe ka Baal-Tamar. Mando kw'anọng p'Israẹl abin k'obe fa bẹ achubh, arenga k'okhubha kw'ewuchen em-edimi ka Gibea ayin ka.
\v 34 Mando kw'adikkobh p'Israẹl p'akhaam ẹfa, anọng nnọhna ẹrọbh obhiri azen, akwu arima Gibea abẹ itzitzikha ttara itzitzikha. Wa erima nda ẹgaangi maa, anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin katzini bi, edimi chabẹ dọ em-ekwu mẹ.
\v 35 Mando kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi okhem anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin k'itzitzikha s'anọng p'Israẹl. Mẹ ewu nduma, anọng p'Israẹl afhu anọng pa Bẹnjamin nnọhna arọbh attaan obhiri nttaan obhiri jobh. Wa anọng pa bẹ afhu biphyir ade anọng p'am-atzima akkangkkaang arim egbong.
\v 36 Wa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin an-are bi, bẹ akk'bẹ akhema.
\p Iwa ajinọng p'Israẹl akk'abina aji anọng pa Bẹnjamin, okhuri da iwa bẹ aphe nnam k'anọng p'achubh atzik kẹ ọbaanga Gibea.
\v 37 Wa ajinọng p'achubh atzik abin m'ẹbhar-ẹbhar adim ka Gibea, bẹ anyaami atzima akkangkkaang afhu anọng k'ọdedenmọn makhọra.
\v 38 Ode ch'iwa anọng p'Israẹl akk'mphaari asa ttara anọng p'achubh atzik bi, bẹ asi irorong k'odedenmon s'ivura ichina k'ẹrọng,
\v 39 ifha anọng p'Israẹl abhakhi bẹ abẹ.
\p Wa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin akk'ẹwọr atta ammuma anọng p'Israẹl ekpo maa (bẹ afhu anọng ẹrọbh obhiri jobh), bẹ aben bi, “Mokhema bẹ mach'ira k'echeden e.”
\v 40 K'ogbe kw'iwa irorong in-ittẹwọr ivura k'ẹrọng k'odedenmon, anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin an-abhakhi are irorong k'odedenmon makhọra s'im-ivura k'ẹrọng.
\v 41 Mando kw'anọng p'Israẹl abhakhi anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin abẹ. Wa ojora anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin, okhuri da iwa bẹ atzini bi, itzama ikk'itta ikhebha bẹ.
\v 42 Mẹ wọ ofon, anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin arọbh k'itzitzikha s'anọng p'Israẹl achina k'okhubha kw'ibe s'anọng an-arukhi, yina, bẹ kafha arọbh anaanga egbong. Mando kw'anọng p'Israẹl p'ayini k'ibhon, akhebh bẹ mẹ afhu.
\v 43 Wa anọng p'Israẹl akhori anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin akhe k'ottem, bẹ akhubh bẹ, abira afha akhọhbha bẹ k'okhubha kw'ewuchen em-eyin ka Gibea.
\v 44 Wa anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin nnọhna arọbh afa obhiri azen, ape. Wa anọng p'ape biphyir ade akkakkaama.
\v 45 Mada ajinọng pa Bẹnjamin p'arikhi abhakhi nnam arọbh achina k'okhubha kw'ibe s'anọng an-arukhi k'itzakpa sa Rimọn, anọng p'Israẹl afhu ajinọng nnọhna jobh obhiri mfa obhiri arọbh jobh k'ọkadeden. Bẹ achina ororo akhubh anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin maa, bẹ apyiri ka Gidom, bẹ abira afhu anọng nnọhna nzen.
\p 
\v 46 M'ewu nduma, ajinọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin, p'am-atzima akkangkkaang arima egbong, anọng nnọhna arọbh attaan obhiri mfa obhiri arọbh jobh, ape. Wa anọng biphyir p'ape ade akkakkaama.
\v 47 Wa anọng ẹnọhna obhiri arọbh jobh abhakhi arọbh, achina k'ibe s'anọng an-arukhi k'itzakpa sa Rimọn, bẹ awobha mẹ k'aphe anna.
\v 48 Mando kw'ajinọng p'Israẹl akpa nnam k'ẹkhọma ch'anọng pa Bẹnjamin, atza atzima ọkkaangkkaang afhu anọng k'ibhon biphyir ọmaana etzirakpo ttara ọttọhk kpenamkpen fa bẹ are. Be akhe ibhon kpenamkpen sa bẹ are ekpon.
\c 21
\s1 Anọng p'Israẹl anang ajinọng pa Bẹnjamin panọng pa bẹ aba
\p 
\v 1 Iwa ajinọng p'Israẹl akk'echekhi asa ka Mizpa bi: “Man aminava paman kọtzọkha ọnang ojinọng manda wani kw'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin ọba.”
\v 2 Wa anọng mba achina ka Bẹtẹl, bẹ atza awobha ẹwọr k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, am-abhom akpẹbh k'idọdọkhi maa, ewu ẹha.
\v 3 Bẹ abhom aben bi, “Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, kw'ode Ibinọkpaabyi kw'Israẹl, odik-dema nwa osi yan otto k'Israẹl o? Ma, ẹkhọma dani chaman k'Israẹl ekk'edimi ka man k'ottem e!”
\p 
\v 4 K'ekpebha ch'ewu ehobh mẹ, anọng mba asi ijafọhnibe rani sa bẹ awobh asi nnanga nkwọmisẹ ọmaana nnaanga s'odidiri.
\p 
\v 5 Mẹ wọ ofon, bẹ aben bi, “Bọng ẹkhọma dọ k'ottem kwa ngọma s'Israẹl dọ eni man abẹ ẹtzọni, k'ogbe kw'ira motzobh k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ka Mizpa?” Ode cha bẹ akk'anwọhngi k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi, achekhi bi, ọnọng manda wani kw'obhumi okwukwu, bẹ akhaambi afhẹ-ẹ.
\p 
\v 6 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl akhaama nkkwosisi ttara Bẹnjamin kw'ode ọgbaanotte kwabẹ, aben bi, “Ẹkhọma dani k'ottem kwa ngọma s'Israẹl ekk'edimi mayina e.
\v 7 Morenga yan oror panọng pa mọnang anọnọnga p'arikhi o, da mokk'ochekhi ka che ch'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi bi, man bẹ aminava paman kọnang bi, bẹ aba o?”
\v 8 Mẹ wọ ofon, bẹ abọbh bi, “Bọng ẹkhọma dọ k'ottem kwa ngọma s'Israẹl dọ eni man abẹ ẹtzọni, k'ogbe kw'ira motzobh k'itzitzikha s'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ka Mizpa?” Wa bẹ akwu aronga bi, ọnọng manda wani kw'ofon Jabẹsh-Gilead kw'ọtza ewobha nda kode.
\v 9 Mada bẹ akk'anọng abhikha biphyir, bẹ akwu are bi ọnọng manda wani kw'ofon Jabẹsh-Gilead kode.
\p 
\v 10 Mando kwa bẹ atzọhmi akkakkaama akkakka pabẹ, anọng nnọhna ẹrọbh obhiri jobh ka Jabẹsh-Gilead ttara ndọhna bi, bẹ afhu ọnọng kpenamkpen panọng ọmaana va.
\v 11 Bẹ aben bi, “Ma wo ode odik kwa bọng asi, bọng fhu ajinọng biphyir ọmaana kwanọng kpenamkpen kw'okk'ojinọng oronga.”
\v 12 Mada bẹ apyiri ka Jabẹsh-Gilead, bẹ are aminava ẹnọhna p'ani ajinọng atzim aronga, bẹ atzima bẹ achina k'ibhingabe ka Shilo k'ẹkhọma cha Kenaan.
\p 
\v 13 Iwa anọng p'Israẹl atzọhm ẹkkaabha ch'ẹmẹm achena anọng p'arikhi k'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin, p'iwa arukhi k'itzakpa sa Rimọn.
\v 14 Mẹ wọ ofon, anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin akpa nnam abhana k'ihọhm sabẹ, bẹ atzọkha aminava mba ẹnọhna pa Jabẹsh-Gilead p'iwa bẹ an-afhu, anang ajinọng mba bẹ aba. Yina, wa aminava mba ajinọng mba biphyir kabeng.
\p 
\v 15 Iwa anọng mba akhaama nkkwosisi ttara Bẹnjamin, okhuri da iwa Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi ọkk'ọphaangi nwa ohokha ka ngọma s'Israẹl.
\v 16 Mẹ wọ ofon, adedennọng p'etzobha nda an-abọbh bi, “Mada bẹ akk'panọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin biphyir afha, morenga yan oror panọng pa mọnang ajinọng p'an-arikhi o?
\v 17 Anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin akhaambi akhaama va pa atzera eho ch'anọng p'arikhi, ifha bẹ aningi ẹkhọma dani ch'Israẹl adimi.
\v 18 Man bẹ aminava paman kọnang bẹ aba, okhuri ọnwọhngi kwa maman anọng p'Israẹl ọkk'ọtzọkha bi: ‘Ẹmma ẹbọkha ọnọng kpenamkpen kw'ọnangi ojinọng kw'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin kwanọng.’
\v 19 Bọng kker e, ọdadaami kwa cho kw'Ọvaar Ibinọkpaabyi owobh ka Shilo, kw'owobh k'ebira-ebira kwa Bẹtẹl, k'okhubha kw'ewuchen em-eyin k'eden ch'echin ka Bẹtẹl ọmaana Shẹkẹm, ttara k'ẹrakha-ẹrakha kwa Lẹbona.”
\p 
\v 20 Iwa bẹ anang anọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin ndọhna, aben bi, “Bọng nọng atza achubha k'iwọni sa grep
\v 21 atzik. Mada aminava pa Shilo ayin ka bi, bẹ akwu attara k'ọkhaana kw'otzubha, ọnọng-ọnọng oyin k'iwoni sa grep, okwu ọbọkha ominanwa wani kw'otzima osi kwanọng kwẹ. Bọng akpa nnam abhana k'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin.
\v 22 Idikha ab'otte ọmaana ab'ọgbaanotte pabẹ apọhr anang man, mọ́gbaak bẹ bi, ‘Bọng si man ọphyaam akkaana bẹ, okhuri da iwa mọni bẹ panọng ọnangi k'ogbe kw'egbong. Bọng oponga-pyibha kw'ọnwọhngi ọvọvọhkhi kàtzọkha, okhuri da iwa bọng ani bẹ aminava pabọng anangi.’ ”
\p 
\v 23 Mando kw'iwa ajinọng p'ẹkhọma cha Bẹnjamin asi. Mada aminava mba am-atzubh ebin, ojinọng kpenamkpen ọbọkha ominanwa wani, otzima osi kwanọng kwẹ. Mando kwa bẹ akpa nnam abhana k'irerek s'ide ekkema chabẹ, bẹ akpa nnam ado ibhon sabẹ, bẹ aruk mẹ.
\p 
\v 24 K'ogbe nwuma anọng p'Israẹl atte ibe nna ọbọhk abhana ka ngọma ọmaana ka nnọmma sabẹ, ọnong-ọnọng k'ekkema chẹ.
\p 
\v 25 K'ogbe nwa, wa anọng p'Israẹl ọvaarnọng kakhaam, wa ọnọng kpenamkpen orukhi akpen k'odem kw'adaakh-ẹ.
